#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&dolphin; is the default file manager by &kde;, designed with usability as a "
"primary focus."
msgstr ""
"&dolphin; je privzeti upravljalnik datotek v &kde;, ki je bil zasnovan tako, "
"da je v ospredju predvsem uporabnost."

#. Tag: keyword
