#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&dolphin; is &plasma;'s default file manager. It aims to improve usability "
"at the user interface level. &dolphin; focuses only on being a file manager "
"whereas &konqueror;, which was &kde;'s default file manager in &kde; 3 and "
"can still be used for file management, is a universal viewer for many file "
"types."
msgstr ""
"&dolphin; je privzeti upravitelj datotek &plasma;. Cilj je izboljšati "
"uporabnost na ravni uporabniškega vmesnika. &dolphin; se osredotoča le na "
"upravitelja datotek, medtem ko je &konqueror;, ki je bil v &kde; 3 privzeti "
"upravitelj datotek v in ga je še vedno mogoče uporabljati za upravljanje "
"datotek, univerzalni pregledovalnik za številne vrste datotek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This design approach allows the developers to concentrate on optimizing the "
"user interface for the specific task of file management."
msgstr ""
"Ta pristop k zasnovi omogoča razvijalcem, da se osredotočijo na optimizacijo "
"uporabniškega vmesnika za posebno nalogo upravljanja datotek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please report any problems or feature requests to the &dolphin; author via "
"the bug report dialog. This is accessible either from the "
"<guibutton>Control</guibutton> button at the right of the toolbar in the "
"default mode without menubar; or from <menuchoice><guimenu>Help</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Report Bug...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu of the "
"application, if the menubar is shown."
msgstr ""
"Prosimo, da o morebitnih težavah ali zahtevah po funkcijah obvestite "
"&dolphin; avtorja prek pogovornega okna za poročilo o napakah. To je "
"dostopno z gumbom <guibutton>Nadzor</guibutton> na desni strani orodne "
"vrstice v privzetem načinu brez menijske vrstice; ali iz menija "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prijavi napako ...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> aplikacije, če je prikazana menijska vrstica."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &dolphin;"
msgstr "Uporaba &dolphin;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "&dolphin; User Interface"
msgstr "&dolphin; Uporabniški vmesnik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "The screenshot below shows &dolphin;'s default user interface:"
msgstr ""
"Spodnji posnetek zaslona prikazuje &dolphin;ov privzeti uporabniški vmesnik :"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of &dolphin;'s default user interface"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona &dolphin;ovega privzetega uporabniškega vmesnika"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&dolphin;'s default user interface.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&dolphin;ov privzeti uporabniški vmesnik.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>&dolphin;'s default user interface.</para>"
msgstr "<para>&dolphin;ov privzeti uporabniški vmesnik.</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid "The elements of the default user interface are:"
msgstr "Elementi privzetega uporabniškega vmesnika so:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The toolbar, which can be used for quick access to frequently used actions. "
"The toolbar can be customized by clicking it with the &RMB; and choosing "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Configure Toolbars...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"from the context menu, with <guimenuitem>Configure Toolbars...</guimenuitem> "
"from the <guibutton>Control</guibutton> button at the right of the toolbar "
"or via <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure "
"Toolbars...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the main menu."
msgstr ""
"Orodna vrstica, ki jo lahko uporabite za hiter dostop do pogosto "
"uporabljenih dejanj. Orodno vrstico lahko prilagodite tako, da jo kliknete z "
"&RMB; in izbiro <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj orodne vrstice...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> v vsebinskem meniju, s <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"orodne vrstice...</guimenuitem> z gumbom <guibutton>Nadzor</guibutton> na "
"desni strani orodne vrstice ali preko <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj orodne vrstice...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> v glavnem meniju."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:156 index.docbook:267 index.docbook:297
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of &dolphin;'s toolbar"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona &dolphin;ove orodne vrstice"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "The default toolbar."
msgstr "Privzeta orodna vrstica."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toolbar items where the icon is sufficient for knowing the command do not "
"have text alongside the icons. This can be changed by a &RMB; click and "
"selecting the item text below <guilabel>Show Text</guilabel>. The "
"<guibutton>Control</guibutton> button at the right side of the toolbar is "
"only displayed if the menubar is hidden."
msgstr ""
"Elementi orodne vrstice, kjer ikona zadostuje za poznavanje ukaza, nimajo "
"besedila poleg ikon. To lahko spremenite z &RMB; kliknite in izberite "
"besedilo elementa pod <guilabel>Prikaži besedilo</guilabel>. Gumb "
"<guibutton>Nadzor</guibutton> na desni strani orodne vrstice je prikazan le, "
"če je menijska vrstica skrita."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The location bar, which always displays the path to the current folder. It "
"can be switched between two different modes, see the <link linkend="
"\"location-bar\">section on the location bar</link> for details."
msgstr ""
"Lokacijska vrstica, ki vedno prikazuje pot do trenutne mape. Preklapljate ga "
"lahko med dvema različnima načinoma, za podrobnosti glejte <link linkend="
"\"location-bar\">razdelek v lokacijski vrstici</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <link linkend=\"dolphin-view\">view</link>, which shows all files and "
"folders in the current folder."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"dolphin-view\">Pogled</link>, ki prikazuje vse datoteke in "
"mape v trenutni mapi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <link linkend=\"places-panel\"><guilabel>Places</guilabel> panel</link>, "
"which provides quick access to bookmarked locations and disks or other media."
msgstr ""
"Pult <link linkend=\"places-panel\"><guilabel>K</guilabel></link>, ki "
"omogoča hiter dostop do označenih lokacij in diskov ali drugih medijev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If desktop search and file indexing are enabled in the <guilabel>Desktop "
"Search</guilabel> module in the &systemsettings; the panel provides "
"<guilabel>Recent</guilabel> items and allows you to search for "
"<guilabel>Documents</guilabel>, <guilabel>Images</guilabel>, <guilabel>Audio "
"Files</guilabel> and <guilabel>Video</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Če sta iskanje po namizju in indeksiranje datotek omogočena v modulu "
"<guilabel>Iskanje po namizju</guilabel> v &systemsettings; pult ponuja "
"<guilabel>Nedavne</guilabel> elemente in omogoča iskanje "
"<guilabel>Dokumentov</guilabel>, <guilabel>Slik</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Zvočnih datotek</guilabel> in <guilabel>Videoposnetkov </guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The status bar. It displays the name, size and type of the file which is "
"currently hovered over with the mouse, or the number and size of the files "
"which are selected. At the right, there is a zoom slider that allows you to "
"adjust the size of the icons in the view."
msgstr ""
"Vrstica stanja. Prikaže ime, velikost in vrsto datoteke, nad katero trenutno "
"lebdite z miško, ali število in velikost datotek, ki so izbrane. Na desni "
"strani je drsnik za povečavo, ki omogoča prilagajanje velikosti ikon v "
"pogledu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The menubar (hidden by default), which provides access to all commands and "
"configuration options. See the <link linkend=\"commands-menubar\">Command "
"Reference</link> for a list of all menu commands. The menubar can be toggled "
"with <guimenuitem>Show Menubar</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>M</keycap></keycombo>) from the <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"menu or the <guibutton>Control</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Menijska vrstica (privzeto skrita), ki omogoča dostop do vseh ukazov in "
"konfiguracijskih možnosti. Oglejte si <link linkend=\"commands-menubar"
"\">Referenčni opis ukazov</link> za seznam vseh menijskih ukazov. Menijsko "
"vrstico lahko preklapljate z <guimenuitem>Pokaži menijsko vrstico</"
"guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>M</keycap></"
"keycombo>) v meniju <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> ali gumb "
"<guibutton>Nadzor</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the menubar is hidden, all its actions are available from the "
"<guibutton>Control</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Če je menijska vrstica skrita, so vsa dejanja na voljo z gumbom "
"<guibutton>Nadzor</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The additional <guilabel>Information</guilabel>, <guilabel>Folders</"
"guilabel> and <guilabel>Terminal</guilabel> panels are hidden by default, "
"for more information see <link linkend=\"panels\"><guilabel>Panels</"
"guilabel>.</link>"
msgstr ""
"Dodatni pulti <guilabel>Informacije</guilabel>, <guilabel>Mape</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Terminal</guilabel> so privzeto skriti, za več informacij glejte "
"<link linkend=\"panels\"><guilabel>pulte </guilabel>.</link>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &dolphin; View"
msgstr "&dolphin; Pogled"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the View"
msgstr "Uporaba Pogleda"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The view displays all files and folders in the current folder. These items "
"can be accessed or manipulated in different ways:"
msgstr ""
"Pogled prikaže vse datoteke in mape v trenutni mapi. Do teh predmetov je "
"mogoče dostopati ali z njimi manipulirati na različne načine:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A file or folder can be opened by clicking it with the &LMB; (or double-"
"clicking, if <guilabel>Open by double-clicking instead</guilabel> is enabled "
"in the &systemsettings; in the <menuchoice><guimenu>Workspace</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>General Behavior</guimenuitem></menuchoice> module)."
msgstr ""
"Datoteko ali mapo lahko odprete tako, da jo kliknete z &LMB; (ali "
"dvokliknete, če je <guilabel>Odpri z dvojnim klikom</guilabel> omogočeno v "
"&systemsettings; v <menuchoice><guimenu>Delovnem prostoru</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Splošno vedenje</guimenuitem></menuchoice> modul)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking any item or the white area around the items with the &RMB; opens a "
"context menu which provides access to many frequently used actions for the "
"item or the current folder, respectively."
msgstr ""
"Klik na kateri koli element ali belo območje okoli elementov z &RMB; odpre "
"kontekstni meni, ki omogoča dostop do številnih pogosto uporabljenih dejanj "
"za element oziroma trenutno mapo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the &LMB; is pressed on an item, but not immediately released, the item "
"can be dragged and dropped in another folder in the current view or in "
"another &dolphin; view (in another &dolphin; window or in the same window if "
"the view is split, see below) to move or copy it or to create a symbolic "
"link. Items can even be dropped in another application to open them in that "
"application."
msgstr ""
"Če &LMB; pritisnete na element, vendar ga ne sprostite takoj, lahko element "
"povlečete in spustite v drugo mapo v trenutnem pogledu ali v drug &dolphin; "
"pogled (v drugem oknu &dolphin; ali v istem oknu, če je pogled razdeljen, "
"glejte spodaj), da ga premaknete ali kopirate ali ustvarite simbolično "
"povezavo. Predmete lahko celo spustite v drugo aplikacijo, da jih odprete v "
"tej aplikaciji."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&dolphin; remembers the history of visited folders. To navigate backward or "
"forward in the history, the corresponding buttons in the toolbar can be used:"
msgstr ""
"&dolphin; si zapomni zgodovino obiskanih map. Za krmarjenje nazaj ali naprej "
"po zgodovini lahko uporabite ustrezne gumbe v orodni vrstici:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Back and Forward buttons in the toolbar."
msgstr "Gumba Nazaj in Naprej v orodni vrstici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Back</guibutton> and <guibutton>Forward</guibutton> buttons "
"in the toolbar can be used to navigate in the history."
msgstr ""
"Z gumboma <guibutton>Nazaj</guibutton> in <guibutton>Naprej</guibutton> v "
"orodni vrstici se lahko pomikate po zgodovini."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you click with the &MMB; the item in the history is opened in a new tab "
"thus keeping the current tab with its content."
msgstr ""
"Če kliknete s &MMB; element v zgodovini se odpre v novem zavihku in tako "
"ohrani trenutni zavihek z vsebino."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid "&dolphin; View Appearance"
msgstr "&dolphin; Ogled videza"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "The toolbar contains buttons to control the appearance of the view:"
msgstr "Orodna vrstica vsebuje gumbe za nadzor videza pogleda:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:303
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>The buttons in the toolbar which control the appearance of the view."
"</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Gumbi v orodni vrstici, ki nadzorujejo videz pogleda.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<para>The buttons in the toolbar which control the appearance of the view.</"
"para>"
msgstr "<para>Gumbi v orodni vrstici, ki nadzorujejo videz pogleda.</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All the settings discussed below and other options concerning, &eg; the "
"sorting of the files in the current folder, can also be modified in the "
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> menu and in the <link linkend=\"view-properties-"
"dialog\">View Display Style dialog</link>. By default, these settings are "
"remembered for each folder separately. This behavior can be changed in the "
"<link linkend=\"preferences-dialog-general\"><quote>General</quote></link> "
"section of the settings."
msgstr ""
"Vse spodaj obravnavane nastavitve in druge možnosti v zvezi z, npr. "
"razvrščanje datotek v trenutni mapi lahko spremenite tudi v meniju "
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> in v <link linkend=\"view-properties-dialog"
"\">pogovornem oknu Pogled sloga prikaza</link>. Privzeto so te nastavitve "
"shranjene za vsako mapo posebej. To vedenje lahko spremenite v razdelku "
"<link linkend=\"preferences-dialog-general\"><quote>Splošno</quote></link> v "
"nastavitvah."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:322 index.docbook:1222
#, no-c-format
msgid "View Modes"
msgstr "View Modes"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first three buttons in the above screenshot switch between &dolphin;'s "
"view modes."
msgstr ""
"Prvi trije gumbi na zgornjem posnetku zaslona preklapljajo med načini "
"pogleda &dolphin;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guibutton>Icons</guibutton> view, which is the default, files will "
"be represented by an icon that visualizes the file type, and a folder icon "
"will be shown for subfolders. The names of folders and files, and the items "
"enabled in <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Additional "
"Information</guisubmenu></menuchoice>, are displayed below the icons."
msgstr ""
"V pogledu <guibutton>Ikone</guibutton>, ki je privzet, bodo datoteke "
"predstavljene z ikono, ki prikazuje vrsto datoteke, za podmape pa bo "
"prikazana ikona mape. Imena map in datotek ter elementi, omogočeni v "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Dodatne informacije</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice>, so prikazani pod ikonami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:338
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Compact</guilabel> view shows the folder contents as icons "
"with the name beside it and the items enabled in <menuchoice><guimenu>View</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Additional Information</guisubmenu></menuchoice> below "
"the name. The items are grouped in columns similar to the <guilabel>Short "
"View</guilabel> in the &kde; file dialog."
msgstr ""
"Pogled <guilabel>Kompaktno</guilabel> prikazuje vsebino mape kot ikone z "
"imenom poleg nje in elemente, omogočene v <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Dodatne informacije</guisubmenu></menuchoice> pod "
"imenom. Elementi so združeni v stolpce, podobne <guilabel>Kratkemu pogledu</"
"guilabel> v oknu &kde; pogovorno okno datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guibutton>Details</guibutton> view, the folder contents are "
"displayed as a detailed list which contains the name, size and last "
"modification time of each item. Additional columns can be added by clicking "
"a column header with the &RMB;."
msgstr ""
"V pogledu <guibutton>Podrobnosti</guibutton> je vsebina mape prikazana kot "
"podroben seznam, ki vsebuje ime, velikost in čas zadnje spremembe vsakega "
"elementa. Dodatne stolpce lahko dodate tako, da kliknete glavo stolpca z "
"&RMB;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:352
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the context menu of the header line, you can add or remove side padding "
"by checking or unchecking the respective menu item and choose between a "
"custom or automatic column width. Automatic width adjusts the width of all "
"columns once to display the longest item in the column completely, except "
"for the <guilabel>Name</guilabel> column where the extension is replaced by "
"<quote>...</quote>"
msgstr ""
"V kontekstnem meniju naslovne vrstice lahko dodate ali odstranite stransko "
"oblazinjenje tako, da označite ali počistite ustrezno postavko menija in "
"izberete med širino stolpca po meri ali samodejno. Samodejna širina enkrat "
"prilagodi širino vseh stolpcev, da v celoti prikaže najdaljši element v "
"stolpcu, razen stolpca <guilabel>Ime</guilabel>, kjer je pripona nadomeščena "
"s <quote>...</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The order of columns can be changed by drag and drop of column headers, "
"except for the <guilabel>Name</guilabel> header, which is always the first "
"column in this view."
msgstr ""
"Vrstni red stolpcev lahko spremenite tako, da povlečete in spustite glave "
"stolpcev, razen glave <guilabel>Ime</guilabel>, ki je vedno prvi stolpec v "
"tem pogledu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:361
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The details view allows you to view the current folder in a tree-like "
"fashion if <link linkend=\"preferences-dialog-viewmodes-details\"> "
"<guilabel>Expandable folders</guilabel></link> are enabled: Each subfolder "
"of the current folder can be <quote>expanded</quote> or <quote>collapsed</"
"quote> by clicking on the <guiicon>></guiicon> or <guiicon>v</guiicon> icon "
"next to it."
msgstr ""
"Pogled podrobnosti vam omogoča ogled trenutne mape v obliki drevesa, če so "
"omogočene <link linkend=\"preferences-dialog-viewmodes-details\"> "
"<guilabel>Razširljive mape</guilabel></link>: Vsaka podmapa trenutno mapo "
"lahko <quote>razširite</quote> ali <quote>strnete</quote> s klikom na ikono "
"<guiicon>></guiicon> ali <guiicon>v</guiicon> poleg nje."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:372
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Grouped View</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Združeni pogled</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:378
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Grouped View</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Združeni pogled</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:380
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All view modes support grouping by the sort type selected in "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Sort by</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"Vsi načini pogleda podpirajo združevanje glede na vrsto razvrščanja, izbrano "
"v <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Razvrsti po</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:389
#, no-c-format
msgid "Information in the View"
msgstr "Informacije v pogledu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:390
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In all view modes &dolphin; shows at least an icon and a name for each item. "
"Using <guisubmenu>Additional Information</guisubmenu> in the <guimenu>View</"
"guimenu> menu or the context menu of the header in <guilabel>Details</"
"guilabel> mode, you can select more information for each item to be shown:"
msgstr ""
"V vseh načinih pogleda &dolphin; prikazuje vsaj ikono in ime za vsak "
"element. Z uporabo <guisubmenu>Dodatne informacije</guisubmenu> v meniju "
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> ali kontekstnega menija glave v načinu "
"<guilabel>Podrobnosti</guilabel> lahko izberete več informacij za vsak "
"element, ki bo prikazan :"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:397
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Size</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Date</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Type</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Rating</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Tags</guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>Comment</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Velikost</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Datum</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Vrsta</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Ocena</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Oznake</guimenuitem> ali <guimenuitem>Komentar</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:403
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Depending on the file type, additionally, sorting criteria can be selected:"
msgstr "Glede na vrsto datoteke lahko dodatno izberete kriterije razvrščanja:"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:405
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Document</guimenuitem>: Number of words and lines"
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Dokument</guimenuitem>: Število besed in vrstic"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Image</guimenuitem>: Size and orientation"
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Slika</guimenuitem>: Velikost in orientacija"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:407
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Audio</guimenuitem>: Artist, album, duration and track"
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Zvok</guimenuitem>: Izvajalec, album, trajanje in skladba"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:411
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guisubmenu>Other</guisubmenu> submenu allows you to select "
"<guimenuitem>Path</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Link Destination</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Copied From</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Permissions</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Owner</guimenuitem> or "
"<guimenuitem>User Group</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Podmeni <guisubmenu>Drugo</guisubmenu> vam omogoča, da izberete "
"<guimenuitem>Pot</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Cilj povezave</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Kopirano iz</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Dovoljenja</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Lastnik</guimenuitem> ali "
"<guimenuitem>Uporabniška skupina</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:421
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preview"
msgstr "Predogled"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:423
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guibutton>Preview</guibutton> is enabled, the icons are based on the "
"actual file or folder contents; &eg; for images a scaled down preview of the "
"image is shown."
msgstr ""
"Če je <guibutton>Predogled</guibutton> omogočen, ikone temeljijo na dejanski "
"vsebini datoteke ali mape; &eg; za slike je prikazan pomanjšan predogled "
"slike."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid "Split"
msgstr "Razdeli"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guibutton>Split</guibutton> is clicked, two views are shown which can "
"display the contents of different folders. This can be convenient for moving "
"or copying files."
msgstr ""
"Če kliknete <guibutton>Razdeli</guibutton>, se prikažeta dva pogleda, ki "
"lahko prikažeta vsebino različnih map. To je lahko priročno za premikanje "
"ali kopiranje datotek."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:445
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting Items in the View"
msgstr "Izbiranje elementov v pogledu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:447
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are several ways to select items in the view. Once a group of items is "
"selected, all actions, such as <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>, <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Move to Trash</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, and drag "
"and drop operations, affect all selected items."
msgstr ""
"Predmete v pogledu lahko izberete na več načinov. Ko je izbrana skupina "
"elementov, se vsa dejanja, kot so <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Izreži</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>, <menuchoice><guimenuitem >Premakni v koš</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> ter operacije povleci in spusti vplivajo na vse izbrane elemente."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:457
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting Items Using the Mouse"
msgstr "Izbiranje elementov z miško"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:461
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can press the &LMB; somewhere in the view and draw a rectangle around a "
"group of items before releasing the button. This will select all items in "
"the rectangle and clear the previous selection. If the &Shift; key is "
"pressed during the selection process, the previous selection is kept."
msgstr ""
"Lahko pritisnete &LMB; kjerkoli v pogledu in narišete pravokotnik okoli "
"skupine elementov, preden spustite gumb. S tem boste izbrali vse elemente v "
"pravokotniku in počistili prejšnjo izbiro. Če  med postopkom izbire "
"pritisnete tipko &Shift;, se ohrani prejšnja izbira."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:468
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the &Ctrl; key is pressed while an item is clicked with the &LMB;, the "
"selection state of this item is toggled. If the &Ctrl; key is pressed while "
"a rectangle is drawn around a group of items as described above, the "
"selection state of all items in the rectangle will be toggled."
msgstr ""
"Če pritisnete tipko &Ctrl;, medtem ko element kliknete z &LMB;, se spremeni "
"stanje izbire tega elementa. Če pritisnete tipko &Ctrl;, medtem ko je "
"pravokotnik narisan okoli skupine elementov, kot je opisano zgoraj, se bo "
"preklopilo stanje izbire vseh elementov v pravokotniku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:475
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the &Shift; key is pressed while an item is clicked with the &LMB;, all "
"items between the previous current item and the clicked item will be "
"selected."
msgstr ""
"Če pritisnete tipko &Shift;, ko element kliknete z &LMB;, bodo izbrani vsi "
"elementi med prejšnjim trenutnim elementom in kliknjenim elementom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:480
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Show selection marker</guilabel> is enabled in the <link "
"linkend=\"preferences-dialog-general-behavior\"><quote>Behavior</quote> tab "
"of the <guilabel>General</guilabel> section of the settings</link>, a small "
"<guiicon>+</guiicon> or <guiicon>-</guiicon> button appears in the top left "
"corner of the item which is currently hovered over with the mouse. Clicking "
"this sign selects or deselects the item, respectively."
msgstr ""
"Če je v zavihku <guilabel>Prikaži označevalnik izbire</guilabel> v zavihku "
"<link linkend=\"preferences-dialog-general-behavior\"><quote>Vedenje</quote> "
"razdelka <guilabel>Splošno</guilabel> nastavitev</link> omogočena možnost "
"<guiicon>+</guiicon> ali <guiicon>-</guiicon>, se v levem zgornjem kotu "
"elementa, nad katerim se trenutno nahaja miška, pojavi majhen gumb <guiicon>"
"+</guiicon> ali <guiicon>-</guiicon>. S klikom na ta znak izberete oziroma "
"odstranite izbiro elementa."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:494
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting Items Using the Keyboard"
msgstr "Izbiranje elementov s tipkovnico"

# Se imena tipk na tipkovnici v tem primeru uporabljajo? Tipke Home, End, page up / down na tipkovnici niso prevedene.
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:498
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If an arrow key, <keycap>Page Up</keycap>, <keycap>Page Down</keycap>, "
"<keycap>Home</keycap>, or <keycap>End</keycap> is pressed, the new current "
"item is selected, and the previous selection is cleared."
msgstr ""
"Če pritisnete smerno tipko, <keycap>Page Up</keycap>, <keycap>Page Down</"
"keycap>, <keycap>Home</keycap> ali <keycap>End</keycap>, je izbrana nova "
"trenutna postavka, prejšnja izbira pa je izbrisana."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:504
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the &Ctrl; key is held while one of the above keys is pressed, the "
"selection remains unchanged."
msgstr ""
"Če med pritiskom ene od zgornjih tipk držite tipko &Ctrl;, izbira ostane "
"nespremenjena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:509
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the &Shift; key is held while one of the above keys is pressed, all items "
"between the previous current item and the new current item will be selected."
msgstr ""
"Če med pritiskom ene od zgornjih tipk držite tipko &Shift;, bodo izbrani vsi "
"elementi med prejšnjim trenutnim elementom in novim trenutnim elementom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:514
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keysym>Space</keysym></keycombo> is "
"pressed, the selection state of the current item is toggled."
msgstr ""
"Če pritisnete <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keysym>Space</keysym></"
"keycombo>, se spremeni stanje izbire trenutnega elementa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:519
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> selects all "
"items in the view."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> izbere vse "
"elemente v pogledu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:524
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> "
"toggles the selection state of all items in the view."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> "
"preklopi stanje izbire vseh elementov v pogledu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:529
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select a file or folder by typing the first few letters of its name and the "
"first matching item is selected. To clear the selection and cancel the "
"keyboard search press &Esc; or wait longer than the timeout of 1 second."
msgstr ""
"Datoteko ali mapo izberete tako, da vnesete prvih nekaj črk njenega imena in "
"izbran je prvi ustrezni element. Če želite izbrisati izbiro in preklicati "
"iskanje po tipkovnici, pritisnite &Esc; ali počakajte dlje od 1 sekunde."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:547
#, no-c-format
msgid "Location Bar"
msgstr "Lokacijska vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:549
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The location bar, which can be found above &dolphin;'s view, displays the "
"path to the current folder. The location bar has two modes."
msgstr ""
"Lokacijska vrstica, ki se nahaja nad prikazom &dolphin;, prikazuje pot do "
"trenutne mape. Lokacijska vrstica ima dva načina."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:555
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bread Crumb Mode"
msgstr "Način kruhovih drobtin"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:557
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <quote>bread crumb</quote> mode, which is the default, each folder "
"name in the path to the current folder is a button which can be clicked to "
"quickly open that folder. Moreover, clicking the <quote>&gt;</quote> sign to "
"the right of a folder opens a menu which allows you to quickly open a "
"subfolder of that folder."
msgstr ""
"V privzetem načinu <quote>kruhove drobtine</quote> je vsako ime mape na poti "
"do trenutne mape gumb, ki ga lahko kliknete, da hitro odprete to mapo. S "
"klikom na znak <quote>&gt;</quote> desno od mape se odpre meni, ki omogoča "
"hitro odprtje podmape te mape."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:565
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the location bar in bread crumb mode"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona lokacijske vrstice v načinu kruhovih drobtin"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:571
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Location bar in bread crumb mode.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Lokacijska vrstica v načinu kruhovih drobtin.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:573
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Location bar in bread crumb mode.</para>"
msgstr "<para>Lokacijska vrstica v načinu kruhovih drobtin.</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:580
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editable Mode"
msgstr "Način za urejanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:582
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When in bread crumb mode, clicking in the gray area to the right of the path "
"with the &LMB; switches the location bar to <quote>editable</quote> mode, in "
"which the path can be edited using the keyboard. To switch back to bread "
"crumb mode, click the check mark at the right of the location bar with the "
"&LMB;."
msgstr ""
"Ko ste v načinu kruhovih drobtin, klik na sivo območje desno od poti z &LMB; "
"preklopi lokacijsko vrstico v <quote>uredljiv</quote> način, v katerem lahko "
"pot urejate s tipkovnico. Če želite preklopiti nazaj na način kruhovih "
"drobtin, kliknite kljukico na desni strani lokacijske vrstice z &LMB;."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:590
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the location bar in editable mode"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona lokacijske vrstice v načinu za urejanje"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:596
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Location bar in editable mode.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Lokacijska vrstica v načinu za urejanje.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:598
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Location bar in editable mode.</para>"
msgstr "<para>Lokacijska vrstica v načinu za urejanje.</para>"

# Kioslave --> kioslaves-i --> kioslave-ov ----> se sklanjatve v tem primeru dodajajo ali ne?
#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:603
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Kioslaves"
msgstr "Uporaba Kioslaves"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:605
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the location bar is empty in editable mode, a drop down box appears in "
"front of the bar listing all available kioslaves on your system. Kioslaves "
"are programs built into &kde; which add support for many different protocols "
"to &dolphin; and other &kde; applications."
msgstr ""
"Če je vrstica lokacije v načinu urejanja prazna, se pred njo prikaže spustno "
"polje s seznamom vseh razpoložljivih kioslaves-ov v sistemu. Kioslaves so "
"programi, vgrajeni v &kde;, ki &dolphin;u in drugim aplikacijam &kde; dodajo "
"podporo za številne različne protokole."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:610
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For example with the <quote>fish</quote> kioslave &dolphin; can be used to "
"manage files and folders on a remote host that is accessible via "
"<acronym>SSH</acronym>. To do this you would type <userinput>fish://"
"username@remotehost</userinput> into the location bar. Similar remote file "
"management can be done on remote hosts accessible via the &FTP;, &NFS;, "
"SFTP, &SMB; (&CIFS;) or webdav protocols."
msgstr ""
"Na primer s <quote>fish</quote> kioslave se &dolphin; lahko uporablja za "
"upravljanje datotek in map na oddaljenem gostitelju, ki je dostopen prek "
"<acronym>SSH</acronym>. To storite tako, da v lokacijsko vrstico vnesete "
"<userinput>fish://username@remotehost</userinput>. Podobno oddaljeno "
"upravljanje datotek lahko opravite na oddaljenih gostiteljih, ki so dostopni "
"prek protokolov &FTP;, &NFS;, SFTP, &SMB; (&CIFS;) ali webdav."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:616
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is also possible to use the kioslaves drop down box to access "
"&systemsettings;, fonts, trash, other programs and devices attached to your "
"computer. See the drop down box for the full list of capabilities available "
"from kioslaves on your system."
msgstr ""
"V spustnem oknu kioslave lahko dostopate tudi do &systemsettings;, pisav, "
"smeti, drugih programov in naprav, priključenih na računalnik. V spustnem "
"oknu si oglejte celoten seznam zmožnosti, ki so na voljo v kiosklavih v "
"vašem sistemu."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:621
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the list of kioslaves"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona seznama kioslave"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:627
#, no-c-format
msgid "Location bar showing list of available kioslaves."
msgstr "Lokacijska vrstica, ki prikazuje seznam razpoložljivih kioslave."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:629
#, no-c-format
msgid "List of available kioslaves."
msgstr "Seznam razpoložljivih kioslave."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:637
#, no-c-format
msgid "Places and Context"
msgstr "Mesta in kontekst"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:639
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the <guilabel>Places</guilabel> panel is hidden; in both modes an "
"additional icon in front of the path is displayed. This icon can be clicked "
"with the &LMB; to open a menu which offers quick access to <quote>places</"
"quote> and storage media. See the <link linkend=\"places-panel\">section "
"about the Places Panel</link> for details."
msgstr ""
"Če je pult <guilabel>Mesta</guilabel> skrit; v obeh načinih se pred potjo "
"prikaže dodatna ikona. To ikono lahko kliknete z &LMB; in odprete meni, ki "
"ponuja hiter dostop do <quote>mest</quote> in medijev za shranjevanje. Za "
"podrobnosti glejte <link linkend=\"places-panel\">poglavje o pultu Mesta</"
"link>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:647
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Location bar with Places icon</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Lokacijska vrstica z ikono Mesta</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:653
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Location bar with Places icon</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Lokacijska vrstica z ikono Mesta</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:658
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The context menu of the location bar offers actions to switch between the "
"modes and to copy and paste the path using the clipboard. Check the last "
"option in this context menu to display either the full path starting with "
"the root folder of the file system or to display the path starting with the "
"current places entry."
msgstr ""
"V kontekstnem meniju lokacijske vrstice so na voljo dejanja za preklapljanje "
"med načini ter za kopiranje in lepljenje poti z uporabo odložišča. Z zadnjo "
"možnostjo v tem kontekstnem meniju lahko prikažete celotno pot, ki se začne "
"s korensko mapo datotečnega sistema, ali pa pot, ki se začne s trenutnim "
"vnosom mesta."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:665
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Location bar context menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Kontekstni meni lokacijske vrstice</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:671
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Location bar context menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Kontekstni meni lokacijske vrstice</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:681
#, no-c-format
msgid "Panels"
msgstr "Pulti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:683
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&dolphin; allows a number of panels to be placed next to the view. These can "
"be enabled in <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Show Panels</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice>. By unlocking the panels and clicking and dragging "
"a panel title, the panel can be moved to a different position, even outside "
"the window."
msgstr ""
"&dolphin; omogoča, da se poleg pogleda postavi več pultov. Omogočite jih "
"lahko v <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Prikaži pulte</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice>. Če odklenete pulte ter kliknete in povlečete "
"naslov pulta, ga lahko premaknete v drug položaj, tudi zunaj okna."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:691
#, no-c-format
msgid "Places"
msgstr "Mesta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:695
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Places</guilabel> panel is located at the left of the window "
"by default. The <guilabel>Places</guilabel> panel shows any locations you "
"have bookmarked. It also shows any disk or media attached to the computer, "
"recently accessed items and allows you to search for certain type of files. "
"The order of these entries can be changed by drag and drop."
msgstr ""
"Pult <guilabel>Mesta</guilabel> je privzeto nameščen na levi strani okna. Na "
"plošči <guilabel>Mesta</guilabel> so prikazana vsa mesta, ki ste jih "
"označili z zaznamki. Prikazuje tudi vse diske ali medije, ki so priključeni "
"na računalnik, nedavno dostopane elemente in omogoča iskanje določenih vrst "
"datotek. Vrstni red teh vnosov lahko spremenite z vlečenjem in spuščanjem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:702
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The easiest way to add a folder to the <guilabel>Places</guilabel> panel is "
"to drag it and drop it in the panel. Moreover, you can click inside the "
"panel with the &RMB; and choose <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Add Entry...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the context menu. The first procedure creates "
"a system wide bookmark, the second procedure can be used to add the current "
"path of the location bar or any desired folder or device. A dialog opens "
"where label, location and icon can be edited and the usage of this entry can "
"be restricted to &dolphin;."
msgstr ""
"Najlažji način dodajanja mape na pult <guilabel>Mesta</guilabel> je, da jo "
"povlečete in spustite na pult. Poleg tega lahko znotraj pulta kliknete z "
"&RMB; in v kontekstnem meniju izberete <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Dodaj vnos..."
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Prvi postopek ustvari sistemski zaznamek, drugi "
"postopek pa lahko uporabite za dodajanje trenutne poti v lokacijsko vrstico "
"ali katero koli želeno mapo ali napravo. Odpre se pogovorno okno, v katerem "
"lahko urejate oznako, lokacijo in ikono ter omejite uporabo tega vnosa na "
"&dolphin;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:712
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A &RMB; click opens the context menu to edit, add, hide or remove entries "
"and change the icon size to one of the predefined values or lock/unlock the "
"panels."
msgstr ""
"S &RMB; klikom se odpre kontekstni meni za urejanje, dodajanje, skrivanje "
"ali odstranjevanje vnosov in spreminjanje velikosti ikone na eno od vnaprej "
"določenih vrednosti ali zaklepanje/odklenjanje plošč."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:715
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The context menu has an action to open the entry in a new tab. Devices can "
"be unmounted using the context menu."
msgstr ""
"V kontekstnem meniju je na voljo dejanje za odprtje vnosa v novem zavihku. "
"Naprave je mogoče odstraniti s pomočjo kontekstnega menija."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:721
#, no-c-format
msgid "Information"
msgstr "Informacije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:723
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Information</guilabel> panel shows extended information about "
"the selected items(s) or about the current folder or the file which is "
"currently hovered over with the mouse, including size, type, and date of "
"last modification. It also features a large preview of the selected item and "
"allows you to assign a rating, tags, and comments to it."
msgstr ""
"Na pultu <guilabel>Informacije</guilabel> so prikazane razširjene "
"informacije o izbranih elementih ali o trenutni mapi ali datoteki, na katero "
"trenutno premikate z miško, vključno z velikostjo, vrsto in datumom zadnje "
"spremembe. Poleg tega je na voljo velik predogled izbranega elementa, ki mu "
"lahko dodelite oceno, oznake in komentarje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:734
#, no-c-format
msgid "Folders"
msgstr "Mape"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:736
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Folders</guilabel> panel shows a tree view structure of the "
"file system. It only shows folders. Clicking a folder with the &LMB; opens "
"this folder in the &dolphin; view."
msgstr ""
"Na pultu <guilabel>Mape</guilabel> je prikazana drevesna struktura "
"datotečnega sistema. Prikazuje samo mape. Če kliknete mapo z &LMB;, se ta "
"mapa odpre v pogledu &dolphin;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:741
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <guilabel>Limit to Home Directory</guilabel> to hide all folders from "
"the tree view except your <guilabel>Home</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <guilabel>Omeji na domači imenik</guilabel>, da iz drevesnega "
"prikaza skrijete vse mape razen <guilabel>Dom</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:747
#, no-c-format
msgid "Terminal"
msgstr "Terminal"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:749
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This panel contains a terminal. The terminal will open at the folder "
"currently shown in the &dolphin; view. Changing the folder in the active "
"&dolphin; view will update the working folder of the terminal. Changing the "
"directory in the terminal will update the working folder in the &dolphin; "
"view. The terminal only works with local media."
msgstr ""
"Ta plošča vsebuje terminal. Terminal se bo odprl v mapi, ki je trenutno "
"prikazana v pogledu &dolphin;. Sprememba mape v aktivnem pogledu &dolphin; "
"bo posodobila delovno mapo terminala. Sprememba imenika v terminalu bo "
"posodobila delovno mapo v pogledu &dolphin;. Terminal deluje le z lokalnimi "
"mediji."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:762
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quick Tips"
msgstr "Hitri nasveti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:764
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following are a number of tips to save time when using &dolphin;."
msgstr ""
"V nadaljevanju so navedeni številni nasveti za prihranek časa pri uporabi "
"funkcije &dolphin;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:769
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quick Bookmarking"
msgstr "Hitro dodajanje zaznamkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:771
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To quickly create a bookmark in the <guilabel>Places</guilabel> panel for "
"the current folder, &RMB; click in the work space and click "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Add to Places</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in the "
"context menu."
msgstr ""
"Če želite hitro ustvariti zaznamek na plošči <guilabel>Mesta</guilabel> za "
"trenutno mapo, &RMB; kliknite v delovnem prostoru in kliknite "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Dodaj v mesta</guimenuitem></menuchoice> v "
"kontekstnem meniju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:778
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The corresponding menu item visibility can be toggled via the <link linkend="
"\"preferences-dialog-context-menu\">&dolphin; context menu settings</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ustrezno vidnost elementa menija lahko preklopite prek <link linkend="
"\"preferences-dialog-context-menu\">&dolphin; nastavitve kontekstnega "
"menija</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:787
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filtering Files"
msgstr "Filtriranje datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:789
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&dolphin; is capable of filtering files, &ie; showing only those items in "
"the view whose name contains a given text. For example, if you wish to show "
"only the <acronym>MP3</acronym> files within a folder, you could filter for "
"<quote>.mp3</quote>. This would then filter out all files whose name does "
"not contain <quote>.mp3</quote>."
msgstr ""
"&dolphin; lahko filtrira datoteke, &ie; prikaže samo tiste elemente v "
"pogledu, katerih ime vsebuje določeno besedilo. Če želite na primer "
"prikazati samo datoteke <acronym>MP3</acronym> v mapi, lahko filtrirate za "
"<quote>.mp3</quote>. Tako bi izločili vse datoteke, katerih ime ne vsebuje "
"<quote>.mp3</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:796
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To filter files, first enable the filter bar, either by pressing <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo> or via the menu: "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Filter...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>. You can then enter the text to be filtered for in the filter "
"bar. The filter bar can be disabled either by pressing &Esc;, or with a "
"&LMB; click on the <guiicon>Hide Filter Bar</guiicon> icon."
msgstr ""
"Če želite filtrirati datoteke, najprej omogočite filtrirno vrstico, in sicer "
"tako, da pritisnete <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></"
"keycombo> ali prek menija: <menuchoice> <guimenu>Urejanje</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Filter...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. Nato lahko v filtrirno "
"vrstico vnesete besedilo, ki ga želite filtrirati. Filtrirno vrstico lahko "
"onemogočite s pritiskom na &Esc; ali s &LMB; klikom na ikono <guiicon>Skri "
"filtrirno vrstico</guiicon>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:807
#, no-c-format
msgid "Finding Files and Searching in Files"
msgstr "Iskanje datotek in iskanje v datotekah"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:810
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&dolphin; is capable of searching for files and for content in files. If "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> is pressed "
"or <menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Search...</guimenuitem> "
"</menuchoice> is used, the <guilabel>Search</guilabel> bar will open already "
"set up to search for files within the current folder and any sub-folders. "
"Start to type into the find input box and the search starts immediately."
msgstr ""
"&dolphin; lahko išče datoteke in vsebino v njih. Če pritisnete <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> ali uporabite "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Išči...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>, se odpre vrstica <guilabel>Išči</guilabel>, že nastavljena za "
"iskanje datotek znotraj trenutne mape in vseh podmape. Začnite tipkati v "
"vnosno polje za iskanje in iskanje se bo takoj začelo."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:817
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Search files and for content in files</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Iskanje datotek in vsebine v datotekah</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:823
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Search files and for content in files</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Iskanje datotek in vsebine v datotekah</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:825
#, no-c-format
msgid "&dolphin; searching files and for content in files."
msgstr "&dolphin; iskanje datotek in vsebine v datotekah."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:829
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The search is case insensitive, and does not require surrounding wildcards "
"(<userinput>*foo*</userinput> and <userinput>foo</userinput> are "
"equivalent), but you can use wildcards inside the search term. <userinput>*</"
"userinput> will match zero or more characters, <userinput>?</userinput> only "
"one single character."
msgstr ""
"Iskanje ne upošteva velikih in malih črk in ne zahteva okoliških nadomestnih "
"znakov (<userinput>*foo*</userinput> in <userinput>foo</userinput> sta "
"enakovredna), lahko pa uporabite nadomestne znake znotraj iskalne besede. "
"<userinput>*</userinput> bo ustrezal nič ali več znakom, <userinput>?</"
"userinput> pa samo enemu znaku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:833
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This feature can be used with running Baloo services; without these services "
"a KIOSlave is launched to provide the search results."
msgstr ""
"To funkcijo lahko uporabljate z delujočimi storitvami Baloo; brez teh "
"storitev se za zagotavljanje rezultatov iskanja zažene KIOSlave."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:835
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The option from <guilabel>Everywhere</guilabel> with activated Baloo "
"services searches in all indexed folders, without Baloo this option starts "
"the search from the user's <replaceable>Home</replaceable> folder."
msgstr ""
"Možnost iz <guilabel>Povsod</guilabel> z aktiviranimi storitvami Baloo išče "
"v vseh indeksiranih mapah, brez storitve Baloo pa ta možnost začne iskanje v "
"uporabnikovi mapi <replaceable>Dom</replaceable>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:839
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Search with More Options</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Iskanje z več možnostmi</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:845
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Search with More Options</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Iskanje z več možnostmi</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:847
#, no-c-format
msgid "&dolphin; searching with More Options."
msgstr "&dolphin; iskanje z več možnostmi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:851
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guilabel>More Options</guilabel> button to extend the "
"<guilabel>Search</guilabel> bar. This provides a very comfortable way for "
"the user to shrink the number of search results."
msgstr ""
"Z gumbom <guilabel>Več možnosti</guilabel> razširite vrstico <guilabel>Išči</"
"guilabel>. Tako lahko uporabnik zelo udobno zmanjša število rezultatov "
"iskanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:855
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To start a search select one or more file types (<guilabel>Documents</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Audio</guilabel>, <guilabel>Video</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Images</guilabel>), a time period, rating, and tag, if you have "
"defined any via <userinput>tag:<replaceable>foo</replaceable></userinput> in "
"the input box."
msgstr ""
"Za začetek iskanja izberite eno ali več vrst datotek (<guilabel>Dokumenti</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Zvok</guilabel>, <guilabel>Video</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Slike</guilabel>), časovno obdobje, oceno in oznako, če ste jo "
"določili prek <userinput>oznaka:<replaceable>foo</replaceable></userinput> v "
"vnosnem polju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:860
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to clear selection using the <guibutton>Clear Selection</"
"guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Izbris izbire je mogoče izčistiti z gumbom <guibutton>Počisti izbrano</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:862
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alternatively you can use these options in the <guilabel>Places</guilabel> "
"panel together with the <guilabel>Filter</guilabel> bar to find files using "
"Baloo or limit the search to files matching the filter expression."
msgstr ""
"Te možnosti lahko uporabite tudi na pultu <guilabel>Mesta</guilabel> skupaj "
"z vrstico <guilabel>Filter</guilabel> za iskanje datotek z uporabo programa "
"Baloo ali omejitev iskanja na datoteke, ki ustrezajo izrazu filtra."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:866
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the Save icon to save a search to the <guilabel>Search For</guilabel> "
"section in the <guilabel>Places</guilabel> panel to quickly access it again "
"in the future."
msgstr ""
"Z ikono Shrani shranite iskanje v razdelek <guilabel>Išči</guilabel> na "
"plošči <guilabel>Mesta</guilabel>, da do njega v prihodnosti hitro dostopate."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:870
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guilabel>More Search Tools</guilabel> drop-down list to select "
"other search tools than Baloo."
msgstr ""
"S spustnim seznamom <guilabel>Več orodij za iskanje</guilabel> lahko poleg "
"orodja Baloo izberete tudi druga orodja za iskanje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:876
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mounting Storage Media"
msgstr "Namestitev medija za shranjevanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:878
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A quick way to mount Storage Media is to click on the device in the "
"<guilabel>Places</guilabel> panel. This will mount and open the device in "
"&dolphin;."
msgstr ""
"Hitro lahko namestite medij za shranjevanje tako, da kliknete napravo na "
"plošči <guilabel>Mesta</guilabel>. To bo namestilo in odprlo napravo v "
"&dolphin;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:886
#, no-c-format
msgid "Undo Actions"
msgstr "Dejavnosti razveljavitve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:888
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&dolphin; is capable of undoing changes you have made to files. For example "
"if you moved a file to the Trash, &dolphin; can undo this and move it back "
"to its original location. To undo an action, press <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> or select <menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Undo: (action name)</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> in the "
"menu, &eg; <guimenuitem>Undo: Rename</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"&dolphin; lahko prekliče spremembe, ki ste jih naredili v datotekah. Če ste "
"na primer datoteko premaknili v koš, lahko &dolphin; to prekliče in jo "
"premakne nazaj na prvotno mesto. Če želite razveljaviti dejanje, pritisnite "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> ali v meniju "
"izberite <menuchoice> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Razveljavi: (ime "
"dejanja)</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>, &eg; <guimenuitem>Razveljavi: "
"Preimenuj</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:899
#, no-c-format
msgid "Renaming A Batch Of Files"
msgstr "Preimenovanje serije datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:900
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&dolphin; is capable of renaming a number of files at the same time. Each "
"file will have the file name specified, including a number, &eg;, Image1."
"jpg, Image2.jpg, Image3.jpg. This can be useful, &eg;, for pictures taken "
"with a digital camera."
msgstr ""
"&dolphin; lahko preimenuje več datotek hkrati. Vsaka datoteka bo imela "
"določeno ime datoteke, vključno s številko, &eg;, Slika1.jpg, Slika2.jpg, "
"Slika3.jpg. To je lahko koristno &eg;, za slike, posnete z digitalnim "
"fotoaparatom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:906
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you wish to rename a batch of files, first select the files to be "
"renamed. This can be done by pressing the &LMB; and drawing a rectangle "
"around the files to be renamed before releasing it, or by holding &Ctrl; and "
"clicking each file to be renamed (see <link linkend=\"selection\">Selecting "
"Items in the View</link> for more details on item selection). Then open the "
"batch-rename dialog by pressing <keycap>F2</keycap> or via the File menu: "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Rename...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"Če želite preimenovati paket datotek, najprej izberite datoteke, ki jih "
"želite preimenovati. To lahko storite tako, da pritisnete &LMB; in narišete "
"pravokotnik okoli datotek, ki jih želite preimenovati, preden ga spustite, "
"ali da držite &Ctrl; in kliknete vsako datoteko, ki jo želite preimenovati "
"(glejte <link linkend=\"selection\">Izbira elementov v pogledu</link> za več "
"podrobnosti o izbiri elementov). Nato odprite pogovorno okno za paketno "
"preimenovanje s pritiskom <keycap>F2</keycap> ali prek menija Datoteka: "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Preimenuj...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:916
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Then enter the name you wish to give the files. The # character must be "
"present within the name. The files will then be renamed, where the "
"<userinput>#</userinput> character is replaced by a different consecutive "
"number for each file."
msgstr ""
"Nato vnesite ime, ki ga želite dati datotekam. V imenu mora biti prisoten "
"znak #. Datoteke bodo nato preimenovane, pri čemer bo znak <userinput>#</"
"userinput> nadomeščen z drugo zaporedno številko za vsako datoteko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:922
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If all file extensions in your selection are different, the name of all "
"files can be changed without using a <userinput>#</userinput> placeholder "
"while preserving the file extensions. This is &eg; useful to rename a video "
"file and all associated subtitle files, which have the same filename, but "
"different extensions."
msgstr ""
"Če so vse končnice datotek v vašem izboru različne, lahko ime vseh datotek "
"spremenite brez uporabe nadomestnega elementa <userinput>#</userinput>, pri "
"tem pa ohranite končnice datotek. To je uporabno za preimenovanje video "
"datoteke in vseh povezanih datotek s podnapisi, ki imajo enako ime, vendar "
"različne končnice."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:930
#, no-c-format
msgid "Comparing A Selection Of Files or Folders"
msgstr "Primerjava izbora datotek ali map"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:932
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the &kompare; application is installed, you can use it to see the "
"differences between two files or folders."
msgstr ""
"Če je nameščen program &kompare;, lahko z njim preverite razlike med dvema "
"datotekama ali mapama."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:937
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First select the two files or folders to be compared. Then launch the "
"&kompare; application via the Tools menu: <menuchoice> <guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Compare Files</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. &kompare; "
"will then open showing the differences between the files or folders."
msgstr ""
"Najprej izberite dve datoteki ali mapi, ki ju želite primerjati. Nato "
"zaženite program &kompare; prek menija Orodja: <menuchoice> <guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Primerjava datotek</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. "
"&kompare; se bo odprl in prikazal razlike med datotekami ali mapami."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:950
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring &dolphin;"
msgstr "Konfiguracija &dolphin;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:952
#, no-c-format
msgid "&dolphin; distinguishes two different kinds of settings:"
msgstr "&dolphin; razlikuje med dvema različnima vrstama nastavitev:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:957
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Settings which affect the general behavior of &dolphin;. These can be "
"configured using the <link linkend=\"preferences-dialog\">Preferences "
"Dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitve, ki vplivajo na splošno obnašanje &dolphin;. Te nastavitve lahko "
"konfigurirate z uporabo <link linkend=\"preferences-dialog\">Pogovorno okno "
"Nastavitve </link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:962
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Settings which determine how the contents of a folder are displayed in "
"&dolphin;. These settings are called <link linkend=\"view-properties\">View "
"Display Styles</link> and can be controlled with toolbar buttons, via the "
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> menu, and with the <link linkend=\"view-properties-"
"dialog\">View Display Style dialog</link>. In the default configuration, all "
"folders use the same display style, but &dolphin; can also be configured to "
"remember each folder's display style separately in the <link linkend="
"\"preferences-dialog-general-behavior\"><quote>General</quote> section of "
"the settings</link>."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitve, ki določajo, kako je vsebina mape prikazana v &dolphin;. Te "
"nastavitve se imenujejo <link linkend=\"view-properties\">Slogi prikaza "
"pogleda</link> in jih je mogoče nadzorovati z gumbi v orodni vrstici, prek "
"menija <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> in z <link linkend=\"view-properties-dialog"
"\">Ogled pogovornega okna sloga prikaza</link>. V privzeti konfiguraciji vse "
"mape uporabljajo isti slog prikaza, vendar &dolphin; lahko tudi "
"konfigurirate tako, da si zapomnite slog prikaza vsake mape posebej v "
"razdelku <link linkend=\"preferences-dialog-general-behavior"
"\"><quote>Splošno</quote> v nastavitvah</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:978
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &dolphin; Preferences Dialog"
msgstr "&dolphin; Pogovorno okno Nastavitve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:979
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Preferences Dialog is opened via <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Configure &dolphin;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in the menu "
"in &dolphin;'s main window. The settings are divided into several groups "
"which can be accessed by clicking the corresponding icon on the left of the "
"dialog."
msgstr ""
"Pogovorno okno z nastavitvami se odpre prek <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &dolphin;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> v "
"meniju v glavnem oknu &dolphin;. Nastavitve so razdeljene v več skupin, do "
"katerih lahko dostopate s klikom na ustrezno ikono na levi strani "
"pogovornega okna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:986
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All settings except for the <guilabel>Startup</guilabel> page and the "
"<guilabel>Status Bar</guilabel> tab on the <guilabel>General</guilabel> page "
"are shared with &konqueror; in filemanager mode."
msgstr ""
"Vse nastavitve razen strani <guilabel>Zagon</guilabel> in zavihka "
"<guilabel>Statusna vrstica</guilabel> na strani <guilabel>Splošno</guilabel> "
"so v skupni rabi z &konqueror; v načinu upravitelja datotek."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:991
#, no-c-format
msgid "General"
msgstr "Splošno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:993
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This group contains settings which control the general behavior of "
"&dolphin;. The group is divided further into four subgroups which can be "
"accessed using the tab bar at the top."
msgstr ""
"Ta skupina vsebuje nastavitve, ki nadzorujejo splošno vedenje &dolphin;. "
"Skupina je nadalje razdeljena na štiri podskupine, do katerih lahko "
"dostopate z uporabo vrstice z zavihki na vrhu."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:999
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the General settings in &dolphin;'s preferences dialog"
msgstr ""
"Posnetek zaslona splošnih nastavitev v &dolphin;ovem pogovornem oknu z "
"nastavitvami"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1005
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Settings."
msgstr "Splošne nastavitve."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1007
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Settings in &dolphin;'s Preferences Dialog."
msgstr "Splošne nastavitve v &dolphin; pogovornem oknu z nastavitvami."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1014
#, no-c-format
msgid "Behavior Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Vedenje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1020
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>View</guilabel> section, you can configure whether the same "
"<link linkend=\"view-properties\">view display style</link> is shared among "
"all folders or folders remember their own individual view display styles."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku <guilabel>Pogled</guilabel> lahko konfigurirate, ali je isti "
"<link linkend=\"view-properties\">slog prikaza pogleda</link> v skupni rabi "
"med vsemi mapami ali pa si mape zapomnijo svoje individualne sloge prikaza "
"pogleda."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1026
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Sorting Mode</guilabel> controls how items are sorted in the view. "
"If <guilabel>Natural sorting</guilabel> is enabled, the sort order of three "
"example files will be <orderedlist> <listitem><para>File1,</para></listitem> "
"<listitem><para>File2,</para></listitem> <listitem><para>File10.</para></"
"listitem> </orderedlist> If this option is disabled, the normal alphabetical "
"sorting case sensitive or case insensitive will be used, which leads to the "
"sort order"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Način razvrščanja</guilabel> nadzoruje, kako so elementi "
"razvrščeni v pogledu. Če je omogočeno <guilabel>Naravno razvrščanje</"
"guilabel>, bo vrstni red treh primerov datotek <orderedlist> "
"<listitem><para>Datoteka1,</para></listitem> <listitem><para>Datoteka2,</"
"para></listitem> <listitem><para>Datoteka10.</para></listitem> </"
"orderedlist> Če je ta možnost onemogočena, bo uporabljeno običajno abecedno "
"razvrščanje, ki razlikuje med velikimi ali velikimi črkami, kar vodi do "
"vrstni red"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1038
#, no-c-format
msgid "File1,"
msgstr "Datoteka1,"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1039
#, no-c-format
msgid "File10,"
msgstr "Datoteka10,"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1040
#, no-c-format
msgid "File2."
msgstr "Datoteka2."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1044
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When hovering over a file or folder with the mouse, a small window with "
"relevant information is shown if <guilabel>Show tooltips</guilabel> is "
"enabled."
msgstr ""
"Ko se z miško pomaknete nad datoteko ali mapo, se prikaže majhno okno z "
"ustreznimi informacijami, če je omogočeno <guilabel>Pokaži opise orodij</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1049
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show selection marker</guilabel> shows a small <guibutton>+</"
"guibutton> or <guibutton>-</guibutton> button above an item's icon if the "
"item is hovered over with the mouse. These can be used to select or deselect "
"the item."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pokaži oznako izbire</guilabel> prikaže majhen gumb <guibutton>+</"
"guibutton> ali <guibutton>-</guibutton> nad ikono elementa, če se na element "
"pomaknete z miško. Te lahko uporabite za izbiro ali preklic izbire predmeta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1055
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enable <guilabel>Rename inline</guilabel> to use this mode if only one item "
"is currently selected. If this option is disabled or several items are "
"selected, a dialog will be displayed for renaming."
msgstr ""
"Omogočite <guilabel>Preimenuj v vrstici</guilabel> za uporabo tega načina, "
"če je trenutno izbran samo en element. Če je ta možnost onemogočena ali je "
"izbranih več elementov, se prikaže pogovorno okno za preimenovanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1060
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enabling <guilabel>Switch between split panes with tab key</guilabel> allows "
"to switch split views with the &Tab; key."
msgstr ""
"Omogočanje <guilabel>Preklapljanje med razdeljenimi podokni s tipko "
"tabulator</guilabel> omogoča preklapljanje med razdeljenimi pogledi s tipko "
"&Tab;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1064
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Disable <guilabel>Turning off split view closes active pane</guilabel> to "
"close the inactive pane when you are turning off the split view mode, &eg; "
"pressing <keycap>F3</keycap>."
msgstr ""
"Onemogočite <guilabel>Izklop deljenega pogleda zapre aktivno podokno</"
"guilabel>, da zaprete neaktivno podokno, ko izklapljate način deljenega "
"pogleda, &eg; pritiskom <keycap>F3</keycap>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1075
#, no-c-format
msgid "Previews Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Predogledi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1077
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this tab, you can configure for which file types previews are shown. "
"Moreover, the maximum size of local and remote files for which previews are "
"generated can be chosen."
msgstr ""
"V tem zavihku lahko konfigurirate, za katere vrste datotek so prikazani "
"predogledi. Poleg tega je mogoče izbrati največjo velikost lokalnih in "
"oddaljenih datotek, za katere se ustvarijo predogledi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1081
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If previews are enabled for folders, previews of some files in the folder "
"will be shown inside a folder's icon."
msgstr ""
"Če so predogledi omogočeni za mape, bodo predogledi nekaterih datotek v mapi "
"prikazani znotraj ikone mape."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1088
#, no-c-format
msgid "Confirmations Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek potrditve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1089
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the ask for confirmation section, you can enable warning dialogs that are "
"shown before potentially harmful actions."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku z vprašanjem za potrditev lahko omogočite opozorilna pogovorna "
"okna, ki so prikazana pred morebitnimi škodljivimi dejanji."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1093
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is also possible to choose the default action <guilabel>When opening an "
"executable file</guilabel>. There are three options, namely "
"<guimenuitem>Always ask</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Open in application</"
"guimenuitem>, and <guimenuitem>Run script</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Možno je tudi izbrati privzeto dejanje <guilabel>Pri odpiranju izvršljive "
"datoteke</guilabel>. Na voljo so tri možnosti, in sicer <guimenuitem>Vedno "
"vprašaj</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Odpri v aplikaciji</guimenuitem> in "
"<guimenuitem>Zaženi skripto</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1096
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The confirmation settings for <guilabel>Moving files or folders to trash</"
"guilabel> and <guilabel>Deleting files or folders</guilabel> affect file "
"operations in &dolphin;, &konqueror;, &gwenview; and all &kde; applications "
"using the default &kde; file dialog, whereas <guilabel>Closing Dolphin "
"windows with multiple tabs</guilabel> is a &dolphin; specific setting."
msgstr ""
"Potrditvene nastavitve za <guilabel>Premikanje datotek ali map v koš</"
"guilabel> in <guilabel>Brisanje datotek ali map</guilabel> vpliva na "
"operacije datotek v &dolphin;, &konqueror;, &gwenview; in vse &kde; "
"aplikacije, ki uporabljajo privzeto &kde; pogovorno okno datoteke, medtem ko "
"je <guilabel>Zapiranje oken Dolphin z več zavihki</guilabel> &dolphin; "
"posebna nastavitev."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1104
#, no-c-format
msgid "Status Bar Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Vrstica stanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this tab, some additional items can be enabled for the status bar, "
"provided the status bar is wide enough:"
msgstr ""
"V tem zavihku lahko omogočite nekatere dodatne elemente za statusno vrstico, "
"če je statusna vrstica dovolj široka:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Show status bar</guilabel> item can be used for toggling "
"status bar visibility."
msgstr ""
"Element <guilabel>Pokaži vrstico stanja</guilabel> lahko uporabite za "
"preklop vidnosti vrstice stanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1116
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Show zoom slider</guilabel> item allows switching visibility "
"of the icon size widget."
msgstr ""
"Element <guilabel>Pokaži drsnik za povečavo</guilabel> omogoča preklop "
"vidnosti pripomočka za velikost ikon."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Show space information</guilabel> item can be used to switch "
"on and off a bar that shows how much space is free on the current drive."
msgstr ""
"Element <guilabel>Pokaži informacije o prostoru</guilabel> lahko uporabite "
"za vklop in izklop vrstice, ki prikazuje, koliko prostora je na trenutnem "
"pogonu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1133
#, no-c-format
msgid "Startup"
msgstr "Zagon"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This group contains settings which control the appearance of &dolphin; on "
"startup."
msgstr ""
"Ta skupina vsebuje nastavitve, ki nadzorujejo videz &dolphin; na začetku."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1139
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Startup settings in &dolphin;'s preferences dialog"
msgstr ""
"Posnetek zaslona nastavitev zagona v &dolphin;ovem pogovornem oknu z "
"nastavitvami"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1145
#, no-c-format
msgid "Startup Settings."
msgstr "Zagonske nastavitve."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1147
#, no-c-format
msgid "Startup Settings in &dolphin;'s Preferences Dialog."
msgstr "Nastavitve zagona v &dolphin;ovem pogovornem oknu z nastavitvami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Show on startup</guilabel> option allows choosing the folder "
"which is opened on startup."
msgstr ""
"Z možnostjo <guilabel>Pokaži ob zagonu</guilabel> lahko izberete mapo, ki se "
"odpre ob zagonu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the <guimenuitem>Folders, tabs, and window state from last time</"
"guimenuitem> item is selected then"
msgstr ""
"Če je izbrana postavka <guimenuitem>Stanje map, zavihkov in oken od zadnjič</"
"guimenuitem>, potem"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When launched from the &GUI; or CLI without any &URL;s, &dolphin; restores "
"session"
msgstr "Ko se zažene iz &GUI; ali CLI brez &URL;jev, &dolphin; obnovi sejo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When rebooting with &dolphin; open, it restores session normally after the "
"system comes back"
msgstr ""
"Pri ponovnem zagonu z odprtim &dolphin;om, se po vrnitvi sistema seja "
"normalno obnovi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When launched with &URL;s, &dolphin; window is opened showing those &URL;s "
"instead of restoring session"
msgstr ""
"Pri zagonu z &URL;ji se odpre okno &dolphin;, ki prikazuje te &URL;je, "
"namesto da bi obnovil sejo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1170
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When &dolphin; is already running and a new window is opened, that new "
"window shows a single tab with the same &URL; as was visible in the "
"previously-open &dolphin; instance"
msgstr ""
"Ko je program &dolphin; že zagnan in se odpre novo okno, se v tem novem oknu "
"prikaže en sam zavihek z istim &URL; kot je bil viden v prej odprtem "
"&dolphin; primeru"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1173
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The location of the folder can also be entered directly or chosen in a "
"dialog which can be opened by clicking the button showing a <quote>folder</"
"quote> icon. Moreover, the current location or the default location (which "
"is the user's home folder) can be used as the startup folder by clicking the "
"corresponding button."
msgstr ""
"Lokacijo mape lahko vnesete tudi neposredno ali jo izberete v pogovornem "
"oknu, ki ga odprete s klikom na gumb z ikono <quote>mape</quote>. Poleg tega "
"lahko kot zagonsko mapo s klikom na ustrezen gumb uporabite trenutno "
"lokacijo ali privzeto lokacijo (ki je uporabnikova domača mapa)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Begin in split view mode</guilabel> controls if the <link linkend="
"\"dolphin-view\">&dolphin; view</link> is split on startup or not for new "
"windows."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Začetek v načinu razdeljenega pogleda</guilabel> nadzoruje, ali se "
"<link linkend=\"dolphin-view\">&dolphin; pogled</link> ob zagonu novih oken "
"razdeli ali ne."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show filter bar</guilabel> controls if the filter bar is shown on "
"startup or not. See the <link linkend=\"filter-files\">section on the filter "
"bar</link> for details."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pokaži filtrirno vrstico</guilabel> določa, ali se filtrirna "
"vrstica prikaže ob zagonu ali ne. Za podrobnosti glejte <link linkend="
"\"filter-files\">poglavje o vrstici filtrov</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Make location bar editable</guilabel> controls if the location bar "
"is in editable mode on startup. The bread crumb mode of the location bar is "
"used otherwise. See the <link linkend=\"location-bar\">section about the "
"location bar</link> for details about the two modes."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Dovoli urejanje lokacijske vrstice</guilabel> določa, ali je ob "
"zagonu lokacijska vrstica v načinu za urejanje. V nasprotnem primeru se "
"uporablja način kruhovih drobtin v lokacijski vrstici. Podrobnosti o obeh "
"načinih najdete v <link linkend=\"location-bar\">poglavju o lokacijski "
"vrstici</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Open new folders in tabs</guilabel> controls whether &dolphin; "
"should open a new folder in a new tab of the current instance when called "
"externally. If not enabled, the new folders will be opened in new instances "
"of &dolphin;. By default this option is enabled."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Odpri nove mape v zavihkih</guilabel> nadzira, ali naj &dolphin; "
"ob zunanjem klicu odpre novo mapo v novem zavihku trenutnega primera. Če to "
"ni omogočeno, se bodo nove mape odprle v novih primerih &dolphin;. Privzeto "
"je ta možnost omogočena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Show full path inside location bar</guilabel> is enabled, the "
"full path of the current location is shown in the bread crumb mode of the "
"location bar. Otherwise, a shortened version of the path is shown if it "
"begins with the path of one of the places in the <guilabel>Places</guilabel> "
"panel."
msgstr ""
"Če je omogočena možnost <guilabel>Pokaži celotno pot v vrstici z lokacijo</"
"guilabel>, je celotna pot do trenutne lokacije prikazana v načinu kruhovih "
"drobtin v vrstici z lokacijo. V nasprotnem primeru se prikaže skrajšana "
"različica poti, če se začne s potjo enega od krajev na plošči "
"<guilabel>Mesta</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show full path in title bar</guilabel> makes it easy to "
"distinguish between files or folders with the same name in different folders."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Prikaži celotno pot v naslovni vrstici</guilabel> omogoča lažje "
"razlikovanje med datotekami ali mapami z enakim imenom v različnih mapah."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1224
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This group contains settings which control the behavior of &dolphin;'s view "
"modes. The three view modes (Icons, Compact, and Details) are accessible via "
"the tab bar at the top."
msgstr ""
"Ta skupina vsebuje nastavitve, ki nadzorujejo obnašanje načinov prikaza "
"&dolphin;. Do treh načinov prikaza (Ikone, Kompaktno in Podrobnosti) lahko "
"dostopate prek vrstice z zavihki na vrhu."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1230
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Icons View settings in &dolphin;'s preferences dialog"
msgstr ""
"Posnetek zaslona nastavitev Pogled ikon v &dolphin;ovem pogovornem oknu z "
"nastavitvami"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1236
#, no-c-format
msgid "View Modes Settings."
msgstr "Nastavitve načinov pogleda."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1238
#, no-c-format
msgid "View Modes Settings in &dolphin;'s Preferences Dialog."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitve načinov pogleda v &dolphin;ovem pogovornem oknu z nastavitvami."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1245
#, no-c-format
msgid "Common settings for all view modes"
msgstr "Skupne nastavitve za vse načine pogleda"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1247
#, no-c-format
msgid "All three view modes have some common settings:"
msgstr "Vsi trije načini prikaza imajo nekaj skupnih nastavitev:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sliders which control the size of the icons. The <guilabel>Default</"
"guilabel> or <guilabel>Preview</guilabel> sizes are used if previews are "
"disabled or enabled, respectively. Note that the icon size can be changed "
"easily with the zoom slider in the status bar if the corresponding option is "
"enabled in the <link linkend=\"preferences-dialog-general-statusbar"
"\"><quote>General</quote> section of the settings</link>."
msgstr ""
"Drsniki, ki določajo velikost ikon. Velikost <guilabel>Privzeto</guilabel> "
"ali <guilabel>Predogled</guilabel> se uporabita, če so predogledi "
"onemogočeni oziroma omogočeni. Upoštevajte, da lahko velikost ikone "
"preprosto spremenite z drsnikom za povečavo v vrstici stanja, če je "
"omogočena ustrezna možnost v razdelku <link linkend=\"preferences-dialog-"
"general-statusbar\"><quote>Splošno</quote> nastavitev</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1261
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A setting for the font used in the view mode: either the system font or a "
"custom font can be chosen."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitev za pisavo, ki se uporablja v načinu prikaza: izberete lahko "
"sistemsko pisavo ali pisavo po meri."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The other settings in the <guilabel>Text</guilabel> section which apply to "
"only one of the view modes are discussed below."
msgstr ""
"Druge nastavitve v razdelku <guilabel>Besedilo</guilabel>, ki veljajo samo "
"za enega od načinov prikaza, so obravnavane v nadaljevanju."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1275
#, no-c-format
msgid "Icons"
msgstr "Ikone"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1278
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Width</guilabel> controls the minimum width that is reserved for "
"the text of a file item."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Širina</guilabel> določa najmanjšo širino, ki je rezervirana za "
"besedilo elementa datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Maximum lines</guilabel> means maximum number of text lines below "
"the icon."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Največje število vrstic</guilabel> pomeni največje število vrstic "
"besedila pod ikono."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1290
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compact"
msgstr "Kompaktno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1293
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Maximum width</guilabel> controls the maximum width that is "
"reserved for the text of a file item."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Maksimalna širina</guilabel> določa največjo širino, ki je "
"rezervirana za besedilo elementa datoteke."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1302
#, no-c-format
msgid "Details"
msgstr "Podrobnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Expandable folders</guilabel> determines whether any folders that "
"have subfolders are displayed in a tree view, where the sub items can be "
"expanded by &LMB; clicking the <guiicon>&gt;</guiicon> icon and collapsed by "
"clicking the <guiicon>v</guiicon> icon."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Razširljive mape</guilabel> določa, ali so mape, ki imajo podmape, "
"prikazane v drevesnem pogledu, pri čemer je podmape mogoče razširiti s "
"klikom ikone <guiicon>&gt;</guiicon> in jih razširiti s klikom ikone "
"<guiicon>v</guiicon>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Folder size</guilabel> allows defining the property to use for "
"sorting folders by their size. It is possible to sort folders by number of "
"items by choosing <guilabel>Show number of items</guilabel> or by the size "
"of the contents by choosing <guilabel>Show size of contents</guilabel>. The "
"recursion level can be limited, which can be useful to constrain unneeded "
"iterations in deep folder structures or on slow file systems. It is also "
"possible to disable displaying folder size by choosing <guilabel>Show no "
"size</guilabel> (which might improve performance in rare cases, however "
"impacts other features like sorting)."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Velikost mape</guilabel> omogoča določanje lastnosti za "
"razvrščanje map po velikosti. Mape so lahkorazvrščene po številu elementov, "
"tako da izberete <guilabel>Prikaži število elementov</guilabel> ali po "
"velikosti vsebine, tako da izberete <guilabel>Prikaži velikost vsebine</"
"guilabel>. Raven rekurzije je lahko omejena, kar je lahko koristno za "
"omejitev nepotrebnih iteracij v globokih strukturah map ali v počasnih "
"datotečnih sistemih. Prav tako je možno onemogočiti prikazovanje velikosti "
"mape z izbiro <guilabel>Pokaži brez velikosti</guilabel> (kar lahko v redkih "
"primerih izboljša zmogljivost, vendar vpliva na druge funkcije, kot je "
"razvrščanje)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1316
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Date style</guilabel> option can be used to configure the mode "
"to display dates in &dolphin;. It is possible to choose between "
"<guilabel>Relative</guilabel> (&eg;, <quote>Yesterday, 3:00pm</quote>) or "
"<guilabel>Absolute</guilabel> (&eg;, <quote>2020-12-23 15:00</quote>)."
msgstr ""
"Z možnostjo <guilabel>Slog datuma</guilabel> lahko nastavite način prikaza "
"datumov v &dolphin;. Mogoče je izbirati med <guilabel>Relativno</guilabel> "
"(&eg;, <quote>Včeraj, 15:00</quote>) ali <guilabel>Absolutno</guilabel> "
"(&eg;, <quote>23.12.2020 15:00</quote>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1327
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigation"
msgstr "Navigacija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This group contains settings which control how navigation in the folder "
"structure and in archives works."
msgstr ""
"Ta skupina vsebuje nastavitve, ki določajo delovanje navigacije v strukturi "
"map in arhivov."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1334
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Navigation settings in &dolphin;'s preferences dialog"
msgstr ""
"Posnetek zaslona nastavitev navigacije v &dolphin;ovem pogovornem oknu z "
"nastavitvami"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1340
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigation Settings."
msgstr "Nastavitve krmiljenja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1342
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigation Settings in &dolphin;'s Preferences Dialog."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitve krmiljenja v v &dolphin;ovem pogovornem oknu z nastavitvami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1348
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The option to open items with a single or double mouse click is a system "
"wide setting and can be changed in the &systemsettings; in the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Workspace</guimenu> <guimenuitem>General Behavior</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> module."
msgstr ""
"Možnost odpiranja elementov z enim ali dvojnim klikom miške je nastavitev za "
"celoten sistem in jo lahko spremenite v &systemsettings; v modulu "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Delovni prostor</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Splošno vedenje</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1354
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Archives will be opened inside &dolphin;, and not in an external "
"application, if <guilabel>Open Archives as folder</guilabel> is enabled."
msgstr ""
"Če je omogočena možnost <guilabel>Odpiraj arhive kot mape</guilabel>, se "
"bodo arhivi odprli znotraj &dolphin; in ne v zunanji aplikaciji."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1359
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Open folders during drag operations</guilabel> is enabled, "
"dragging an item with the mouse and hovering over a folder with it for a "
"short time will open that folder. This allows you to move or copy items "
"quickly to folders which are several levels deeper in the folder hierarchy."
msgstr ""
"Če je omogočena možnost <guilabel>Odpiranje map med vlečenjem</guilabel>, se "
"ob vlečenju elementa z miško in kratkotrajnem premikanju nad mapo z njim "
"odpre ta mapa. Tako lahko hitro premikate ali kopirate elemente v mape, ki "
"so v hierarhiji map več ravni globlje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1373
#, no-c-format
msgid "Services"
msgstr "Storitve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This group offers a selection of services that can be shown in the "
"<guisubmenu>Actions</guisubmenu> submenu of &dolphin;'s context menu which "
"appears when clicking a file or folder with the &RMB;."
msgstr ""
"Ta skupina ponuja izbor storitev, ki so lahko prikazane v podmeniju "
"<guisubmenu>Dejanja</guisubmenu> kontekstnega menija &dolphin;, ki se "
"prikaže, ko kliknete datoteko ali mapo z &RMB;."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1382
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Screenshot of the Services Menu settings in &dolphin;'s preferences dialog"
msgstr ""
"Posnetek zaslona nastavitev menija Storitve v &dolphin;ovem pogovornem oknu "
"z nastavitvami"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1388
#, no-c-format
msgid "Services Settings."
msgstr "Nastavitve storitev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1390
#, no-c-format
msgid "Services Settings in &dolphin;'s Preferences Dialog."
msgstr "Nastavitve storitev v &dolphin;ovem pogovornem oknu z nastavitvami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1394
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the <guibutton>Download New Services</guibutton> you can fetch "
"additional services for the context menu."
msgstr ""
"Z gumbom <guibutton>Prejmi nove storitve</guibutton> lahko za kontekstni "
"meni pridobite dodatne storitve."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1398
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have installed &dolphin;'s plugins for <guilabel>Bazaar</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Mercurial</guilabel>, <guilabel>Git</guilabel> or "
"<guilabel>Subversion</guilabel> from the kdesdk module these services are "
"shown in the list. If these plugins are enabled and you enter a folder which "
"is under version control, the version state (locally changed, up to date "
"&etc;) is indicated by icons and you have additional entries in the context "
"menu like commit, update, add, remove &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Če ste iz modula kdesdk namestili vtičnike &dolphin; za <guilabel>Bazaar</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Mercurial</guilabel>, <guilabel>Git</guilabel> ali "
"<guilabel>Subversion</guilabel>, so te storitve prikazane na seznamu. Če so "
"ti vtičniki omogočeni in vstopite v mapo, ki je pod nadzorom različic, je "
"stanje različice (lokalno spremenjena, posodobljena &etc;) označeno z "
"ikonami, v kontekstnem meniju pa so na voljo dodatni vnosi, kot so commit, "
"update, add, remove &etc;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1407
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the service list you can also choose if the <guimenuitem>Copy To</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Move To</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Add to "
"Places</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Sort By</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>View "
"Mode</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Open in New Tab</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Open in New Window</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Copy Location</"
"guimenuitem>, and <guimenuitem>Duplicate Here</guimenuitem> commands are "
"shown in the context menu."
msgstr ""
"Na seznamu storitev lahko izberete tudi, ali bodo ukazi <guimenuitem>Kopiraj "
"v</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Premakni v</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Dodaj v "
"mesta</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Sortiraj po</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Način pregleda</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Odpri v novi "
"zavihek</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Odpri v novo okno</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Kopiraj mesto</guimenuitem> in <guimenuitem>Podvoji tukaj</"
"guimenuitem> prikazani v kontekstnem meniju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1415
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&dolphin; has to be restarted to activate the changes for some of these "
"settings."
msgstr ""
"Za aktiviranje sprememb nekaterih nastavitev je treba znova zagnati "
"&dolphin;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1422
#, no-c-format
msgid "Trash"
msgstr "Smeti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1424
#, no-c-format
msgid "This group contains settings which control the behavior of the trash."
msgstr "Ta skupina vsebuje nastavitve, ki nadzorujejo obnašanje smeti."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1428
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Trash settings in &dolphin;'s preferences dialog"
msgstr ""
"Posnetek zaslona nastavitev koša &dolphin;ovem pogovornem oknu z nastavitvami"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1434
#, no-c-format
msgid "Trash Settings."
msgstr "Nastavitve smeti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1436
#, no-c-format
msgid "Trash Settings in &dolphin;'s Preferences Dialog."
msgstr "Nastavitve koša v &dolphin;ovem pogovornem oknu z nastavitvami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1442
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Files which are older than a configurable number of days can be deleted "
"automatically."
msgstr ""
"Datoteke, ki so starejše od nastavljivega števila dni, se lahko samodejno "
"izbrišejo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1446
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The size of the trash can be limited to a configurable percentage of the "
"disk size. If this limit is reached, a warning can be issued, or the oldest "
"or largest files can be deleted automatically."
msgstr ""
"Velikost smeti je lahko omejena na nastavljiv odstotek velikosti diska. Če "
"je ta meja dosežena, se lahko izda opozorilo ali pa se najstarejše ali "
"največje datoteke samodejno izbrišejo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1459
#, no-c-format
msgid "User Feedback"
msgstr "Povratne informacije uporabnikov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1461
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This group contains settings which control your contributing information on "
"the &dolphin; usage to its developers."
msgstr ""
"Ta skupina vsebuje nastavitve, ki nadzorujejo vaše prispevanje informacij o "
"uporabi &dolphin; razvijalcem."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1465
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Screenshot of the User Feedback settings in &dolphin;'s preferences dialog"
msgstr ""
"Posnetek zaslona nastavitev povratne informacije uporabnika v &dolphin;ovem "
"pogovornem oknu z nastavitvami"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1471
#, no-c-format
msgid "User Feedback Settings."
msgstr "Nastavitve povratnih informacij uporabnika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1473
#, no-c-format
msgid "User Feedback Settings in &dolphin;'s Preferences Dialog."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitve povratnih informacij uporabnika &dolphin;ovem pogovornem oknu z "
"nastavitvami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1479
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can contribute some feedback on &dolphin; if you wish. Use sliders to "
"configure your level of participation."
msgstr ""
"Če želite, lahko prispevate nekaj povratnih informacij o &dolphin;. Z "
"drsniki nastavite raven sodelovanja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1492
#, no-c-format
msgid "Folder View Display Style"
msgstr "Slog prikaza pogleda mape"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1494
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following settings control how the contents of a folder are displayed in "
"the &dolphin; view, and are stored on a per-folder basis by default:"
msgstr ""
"Naslednje nastavitve določajo, kako je vsebina mape prikazana v pogledu "
"&dolphin; in so privzeto shranjene za vsako mapo posebej:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1500
#, no-c-format
msgid "The view mode (Icons, Compact, Details)"
msgstr "Način pogleda (Ikone, Kompaktno, Podrobnosti)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1504
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The sorting of items, which is determined by the sort order (ascending, "
"descending) and the attribute (such as name, size,...) that the items are "
"sorted by"
msgstr ""
"Razvrščanje elementov, ki je določeno z vrstnim redom (naraščajoče, "
"padajoče) in atributom (kot so ime, velikost, ...), po katerem so elementi "
"razvrščeni"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1510
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sorting of folders and files &ndash; are folders shown first or not?"
msgstr "Razvrščanje map in datotek &ndash; so mape prikazane prve ali ne?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1514
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Previews &ndash; are they shown instead of icons (based on the settings made "
"in <link linkend=\"preferences-dialog-general-previews\"><guilabel>Previews</"
"guilabel> tab of &dolphin;'s General settings</link>) or not?"
msgstr ""
"Predogledi &ndash; ali so prikazani namesto ikon (na podlagi nastavitev v "
"zavihku <link linkend=\"preferences-dialog-general-previews"
"\"><guilabel>Predogledi</guilabel> v splošnih nastavitvah &dolphin;</link>) "
"ali ne?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1520
#, no-c-format
msgid "Are items shown in groups in the views?"
msgstr "Ali so elementi v prikazih prikazani v skupinah?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1524
#, no-c-format
msgid "Are hidden files shown?"
msgstr "Ali so prikazane skrite datoteke?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1528
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"What additional information (besides the name) is shown in the Icons or "
"Details view?"
msgstr ""
"Katere dodatne informacije (poleg imena) so prikazane v pogledu Ikone ali "
"Podrobnosti?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1533
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The view display style can be configured in the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</"
"guimenu></menuchoice> menu, some (such as the view mode) can also be changed "
"using toolbar buttons."
msgstr ""
"Slog prikaza pogleda lahko nastavite v meniju <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu></menuchoice>, nekatere (na primer način pogleda) pa lahko "
"spremenite tudi z gumbi orodne vrstice."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1540
#, no-c-format
msgid "The View Display Style dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno Slog prikaza pogleda"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1545
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the View Display Style dialog"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona Pogovornega okna Slog prikaza pogleda"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1551
#, no-c-format
msgid "The View Display Style dialog."
msgstr "Pogovorno okno Slog prikaza pogleda."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1553
#, no-c-format
msgid "The View Display Style Dialog."
msgstr "Pogovorno okno Pogled sloga prikaza."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1555
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>View Display Style</guilabel> dialog can be used to quickly "
"modify the view display styles for many folders at once. This is done for "
"the current folder, for the current folder including all subfolders, or even "
"for all folders, depending on the choice made in the <guilabel>Apply to</"
"guilabel> section."
msgstr ""
"S pogovornim oknom <guilabel>Slog prikaza pogleda</guilabel> lahko hitro "
"spremenite sloge prikaza pogleda za več map naenkrat. To se izvede za "
"trenutno mapo, za trenutno mapo z vsemi podmapami ali celo za vse mape, "
"odvisno od izbire v razdelku <guilabel>Izvedi za</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1563
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Use as default view settings</guilabel> is enabled, the chosen "
"view properties will also be used for all folders which do not have "
"customized view properties yet."
msgstr ""
"Če je omogočena možnost <guilabel>Uporabi kot privzete nastavitve pogleda</"
"guilabel>, bodo izbrane lastnosti pogleda uporabljene tudi za vse mape, ki "
"še nimajo prilagojenih lastnosti pogleda."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1576
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Reference"
msgstr "Referenca ukazov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1577
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default the menubar is not shown. All actions described here either can "
"be accessed with toolbar buttons or with items in the menu of the "
"<guibutton>Control</guibutton> toolbar button."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto menijska vrstica ni prikazana. Do vseh tukaj opisanih dejanj lahko "
"dostopate z gumbi orodne vrstice ali z elementi v meniju gumba "
"<guibutton>Nadzor</guibutton> orodne vrstice."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1582
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Menubar in &dolphin;'s Main Window"
msgstr "Menijska vrstica v &dolphin;ovem glavnem oknu"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1585
#, no-c-format
msgid "The File Menu"
msgstr "Meni Datoteka"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1590
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Create New</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Ustvari novo</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1594
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creates a new object (such as a folder or a text file) in the current folder."
msgstr ""
"Ustvari nov predmet (na primer mapo ali besedilno datoteko) v trenutni mapi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1596
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You will find an explanation of all available objects in &konqueror;'s "
"handbook in the chapter <ulink url=\"help:/konqueror/making.html\">Create "
"New</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Razlago vseh razpoložljivih predmetov najdete v priročniku &konqueror; v "
"poglavju <ulink url=\"help:/konqueror/making.html\">Ustvari novo</ulink>."

# .local/share/templates se prevaja?
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1599
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to create your own <guisubmenu>Create New...</guisubmenu> "
"submenu items. Use files from <ulink url=\"https://invent.kde.org/frameworks/"
"kio/-/tree/master/src/new_file_templates\">KIO source repository</ulink> as "
"a reference and put the resulting <filename role=\"extension\">.desktop</"
"filename> file into the <filename role=\"directory\">.local/share/templates</"
"filename> in your home directory (the address can be determined using the "
"<userinput>kf5-config --path templates</userinput> command in &konsole;), "
"then restart &dolphin;."
msgstr ""
"Možno je ustvariti lastne elemente podmenija <guisubmenu>Ustvari novo...</"
"guisubmenu>. Kot referenco uporabite datoteke iz <ulink url=\"https://invent."
"kde.org/frameworks/kio/-/tree/master/src/new_file_templates\">KIO izvorni "
"repozitorij</ulink> in nastalo datoteko <filename role=\"extension\">."
"desktop</filename> vstavite v <filename role=\"directory\">.local/share/"
"templates</filename> v domačem imeniku (naslov lahko določite z ukazom "
"<userinput>kf5-config --path templates</userinput> v &konsole;), nato znova "
"zaženite &dolphin;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1607
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Window</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Novo okno</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1614
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens a new &dolphin; window."
msgstr "Odpre novo &dolphin; okno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1618
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Tab</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nov zavihek</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1625
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens a new tab."
msgstr "Odpre nov zavihek."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1629
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Close Tab</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapri okno</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1636
#, no-c-format
msgid "Closes the current tab."
msgstr "Zapre trenutno okno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1640
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Undo close tab</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Razveljavi "
"zaprtje okna</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1647
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reopens the last closed tab."
msgstr "Ponovno odpre zadnji zaprti zavihek."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1651
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Rename</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Preimenuj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1658
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Renames one currently selected item inline. Opens the <link linkend=\"batch-"
"rename\">batch rename dialog</link> if several items are selected."
msgstr ""
"Preimenuje en trenutno izbrani element v vrstici. Odpre <link linkend="
"\"batch-rename\">pogovorno okno za paketno preimenovanje</link>, če je "
"izbranih več elementov."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1664
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>Del</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Move to Trash</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>Del</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Premakni v smeti</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1671
#, no-c-format
msgid "Moves the currently selected item(s) to the trash."
msgstr "Premakne trenutno izbrane elemente v smeti."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1676
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>Del</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Delete</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>Del</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izbriši</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1683
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Permanently deletes the currently selected item(s). The items are not moved "
"to the trash and cannot be restored."
msgstr ""
"Trajno izbriše trenutno izbrane elemente. Predmeti se ne premaknejo v smeti "
"in jih ni mogoče obnoviti."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1688
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Target</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prikaži tarčo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1692
#, no-c-format
msgid "This action highlights a link target in a new &dolphin; window."
msgstr "To dejanje poudari cilj povezave v novem &dolphin; oknu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1697
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Duplicate Here</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Podvoji tukaj</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1704
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creates duplicates of selected items appending <replaceable> copy</"
"replaceable> to the end of their names."
msgstr ""
"Ustvari dvojnike izbranih elementov in na konec njihovih imen doda "
"<replaceable> kopiraj</replaceable>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1708
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>Return</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Properties</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>Return</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Lastnosti</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1715
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shows the properties dialog for the currently selected item(s)."
msgstr "Prikaže pogovorno okno z lastnostmi za trenutno izbrane elemente."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1720
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izhod</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1727
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exits &dolphin;."
msgstr "Konča &dolphin;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1735
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Edit Menu"
msgstr "Meni za urejanje"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1740
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Razveljavi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1747
#, no-c-format
msgid "Undoes the last action performed by &dolphin;."
msgstr "Razveljavi zadnje dejanje, ki ga je izvedel &dolphin;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1751
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izreži</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1758
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cuts the currently selected item(s)."
msgstr "Izreže trenutno izbrane elemente."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1762
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1769
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copies the currently selected item(s)."
msgstr "Kopira trenutno izbrane elemente."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1773
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Paste Clipboard "
"Contents...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Paste one File</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Paste one Folder</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> or <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Paste x Items</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Urdei</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prilepi vsebino "
"odložišča...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Prilepi eno datoteko</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prilepi eno datoteko</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Prilepi x elemente</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1783
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pastes the currently copied/cut items to the current folder. If the "
"clipboard does not contain files or folders, the clipboard contents (such as "
"text or image data) will be pasted into a new file. The name of this file "
"has to be entered in a dialog."
msgstr ""
"Prilepi trenutno kopirane/izrezane elemente v trenutno mapo. Če odložišče ne "
"vsebuje datotek ali map, se vsebina odložišča (na primer besedilo ali "
"slikovni podatki) prilepi v novo datoteko. Ime te datoteke je treba vnesti v "
"pogovorno okno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1791
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F5</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Copy to inactive split view</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F5</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kopiraj v neaktivni deljeni "
"pogled</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1798
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Copies the currently selected item(s) from the active split view to the "
"inactive split view."
msgstr ""
"Kopira trenutno izbrane elemente iz aktivnega deljenega pogleda v neaktivni "
"deljeni pogled."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1802
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F6</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Move to inactive split view</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F6</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Premakni v neaktivni "
"razdeljeni pogled</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1809
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Moves the currently selected item(s) from the active split view to the "
"inactive split view. Is disabled if the current user does not have write "
"permission on the selected item(s)."
msgstr ""
"Premakne trenutno izbrane elemente iz aktivnega razdeljenega pogleda v "
"neaktivni razdeljeni pogled. Je onemogočeno, če trenutni uporabnik nima "
"dovoljenja za pisanje v izbranem(-ih) elementu(-ih)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1814
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Filter...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Filtriraj...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1821
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Enables and disables the <link linkend=\"filter-files\">filter bar</"
"link>.</action> You can also use the alternate shortcut <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>/</keycap></keycombo> for this action."
msgstr ""
"<action>Omogoči in onemogoči <link linkend=\"filter-files\">filtrirno "
"vrstico</link>.</action> Za to dejanje lahko uporabite tudi nadomestno "
"bližnjico <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>/</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1827
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Search...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Išči...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1834
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens the find bar. Enter a search term into the edit box and select to "
"search for filename or in contents of files starting from the current folder "
"or everywhere."
msgstr ""
"Odpre vrstico za iskanje. V polje za urejanje vnesite iskalni izraz in "
"izberite, ali želite iskati po imenu datoteke ali po vsebini datotek od "
"trenutne mape ali povsod."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1839
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Select All</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izberi vse</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1846
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selects all files and folders in the current folder."
msgstr "Izbere vse datoteke in mape v trenutni mapi."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1851
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>A</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Invert Selection</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>A</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Obrni izbiro</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1858
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selects all unselected items and deselects all selected items in the current "
"folder."
msgstr ""
"Označi vse neizbrane elemente in odstrani vse izbrane elemente v trenutni "
"mapi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1867
#, no-c-format
msgid "The View Menu"
msgstr "Meni Pogled"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1872
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>+</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zoom In</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>+</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Približaj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1879
#, no-c-format
msgid "Increases the size of icons in the view."
msgstr "Poveča velikost ikon v pogledu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1883
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>-</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zoom Out</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>-</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pomanjšaj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1890
#, no-c-format
msgid "Decreases the size of icons in the view."
msgstr "Zmanjša velikost ikon v pogledu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1894
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>0</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zoom Reset</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>0</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ponastavi povečavo</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1901
#, no-c-format
msgid "Resets the size of icons in the view to default."
msgstr "Ponastavi velikost ikon v pogledu na privzeto."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1905
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>View Mode</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Način pogleda</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1909
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Changes the view mode to <guimenuitem>Icons</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>1</keycap></keycombo>), <guimenuitem>Compact</"
"guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>2</keycap></"
"keycombo>) or <guimenuitem>Details</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>3</keycap></keycombo>)."
msgstr ""
"Spremeni način prikaza na <guimenuitem>Ikone</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>1</keycap></keycombo>), <guimenuitem>Kompaktno</"
"guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>2</keycap></"
"keycombo>) ali <guimenuitem>Podrobnosti</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>3</keycap></keycombo>)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1916
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Sort By</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Razvrsti po</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1920
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Changes whether items are sorted</action> by <guimenuitem>Name</"
"guimenuitem> or other criteria described in <link linkend=\"dolphin-view-"
"information\">Information in the View</link>."
msgstr ""
"<action>Spremeni, ali so elementi razvrščeni</action> po <guimenuitem>Ime</"
"guimenuitem> ali drugih merilih, opisanih v <link linkend=\"dolphin-view-"
"information\">Informacije v pogledu</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1922
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Descending</guimenuitem> reverses the sort order. "
"<guimenuitem>Folders First</guimenuitem> sorts folders before files."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Descending</guimenuitem> obrne vrstni red razvrščanja. "
"<guimenuitem>Folders First</guimenuitem> razvrsti mape pred datotekami."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1928
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Show Additional Information</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Prikaži dodatne informacije</"
"guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1932
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Displays additional information</action> described in <link linkend="
"\"dolphin-view-information\">Information in the View</link>."
msgstr ""
"<action>Prikaže dodatne informacije</action>, opisane v <link linkend="
"\"dolphin-view-information\">Informacije v Pogledu</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1938
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Previews</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prikaži predoglede</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1942
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Displays a symbolic preview of the file contents </action> in the "
"different view modes."
msgstr ""
"<action>Prikaže simbolični predogled vsebine datoteke </action> v različnih "
"načinih prikaza."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1947
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show in Groups</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prikaži v skupinah</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1951
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Displays</action> the content of the current folder grouped by the "
"option selected in <guimenuitem>Sort By</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"<action>Prikaže</action> vsebino trenutne mape, razvrščeno po možnosti, "
"izbrani v <guimenuitem>Razvrsti po</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1957
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>.</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Hidden Files</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>.</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prikaži skrite datoteke</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1964
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Shows all the hidden files and sub-folders within the current folder."
"</action>There is an alternate shortcut <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo> for this action."
msgstr ""
"<action>Pokaže vse skrite datoteke in podmape v trenutni mapi.</action>Za to "
"dejanje obstaja nadomestna bližnjica <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1970
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F3</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Split</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F3</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Razdeli</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1977
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enables and disables the split view mode."
msgstr "Omogoči in onemogoči način razdeljenega pogleda."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1981
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F5</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Reload</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F5</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Znova naloži</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1988
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reloads the current folder."
msgstr "Ponovno naloži trenutno mapo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1992
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Stop</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ustavi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:1996
#, no-c-format
msgid "Stops loading/reading the contents of the current folder."
msgstr "Ustavi nalaganje/branje vsebine trenutne mape."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2001
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Show Panels</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Prikaži pulte</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2005
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Enables and disables</action> the different <link linkend=\"panels"
"\">panels</link>: <guimenuitem>Places</guimenuitem> (<keycap>F9</keycap>), "
"<guimenuitem>Information</guimenuitem> (<keycap>F11</keycap>), "
"<guimenuitem>Folders</guimenuitem> (<keycap>F7</keycap>), "
"<guimenuitem>Terminal</guimenuitem> (<keycap>F4</keycap>). With "
"<guimenuitem>Lock Panels</guimenuitem> the panel header with caption and two "
"buttons is hidden to save space and the panels are immutable, with "
"<guimenuitem>Unlock Panels</guimenuitem> the header is visible and the panel "
"can be moved to the right or left or even outside the main window."
msgstr ""
"<action>Vključi in izključi</action> različne <link linkend=\"panels"
"\">pulte</link>: <guimenuitem>Mesta</guimenuitem> (<keycap>F9</keycap>), "
"<guimenuitem>Informacije</guimenuitem> (<keycap>F11</keycap>), "
"<guimenuitem>Mape</guimenuitem> (<keycap>F7</keycap>), "
"<guimenuitem>Terminal</guimenuitem> (<keycap>F4</keycap>). S funkcijo "
"<guimenuitem>Zaklenit pulte</guimenuitem> se zaradi varčevanja s prostorom "
"skrije glavo pulta z napisom in dvema gumboma, pulti pa so nespremenljivi, s "
"funkcijo <guimenuitem>Odkleni pulte</guimenuitem> pa je glava vidna in pult "
"lahko premaknete na desno ali levo ali celo zunaj glavnega okna."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2018
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>F6</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Location Bar</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Editable Location</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>F6</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Lokacijska vrstica</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Lokacijo je možno "
"urediti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:2026
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Changes the location bar between the two modes; the <link linkend=\"location-"
"bar-bread-crumb\">bread crumb mode</link> and the <link linkend=\"location-"
"bar-editable\">editable mode</link>."
msgstr ""
"Spremeni lokacijsko vrstico med dvema načinoma: <link linkend=\"location-bar-"
"bread-crumb\">načinom kruhovih drobtin</link> in <link linkend=\"location-"
"bar-editable\">načinom urejanja</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2033
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Location Bar</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Replace Location</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Lokacijska vrstica</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Zamenjaj lokacijo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:2041
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switches the location bar to <link linkend=\"location-bar-editable"
"\">editable mode</link>, if necessary, and selects the location such that it "
"can be replaced quickly."
msgstr ""
"Preklopi vrstico lokacije v <link linkend=\"location-bar-editable\">način "
"urejanja</link>, če je to potrebno, in izbere lokacijo tako, da jo je mogoče "
"hitro zamenjati."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2047
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Adjust View Display Style...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prilagodi slog prikaza pogleda...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:2051
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens the <link linkend=\"view-properties-dialog\">View Display Style "
"Dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Odpre <link linkend=\"view-properties-dialog\">Dialog za slog prikaza</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2060
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Go Menu"
msgstr "Meni Go"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2065
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>Up</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Up</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>Up</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Idi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Up</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:2072
#, no-c-format
msgid "Changes to the folder above the current folder."
msgstr "Spremeni mapo nad trenutno mapo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2076
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>Left</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Back</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>Left</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Back</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:2083
#, no-c-format
msgid "Changes to the previously viewed folder."
msgstr "Spremeni predhodno ogledano mapo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2087
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>Right</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Forward</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>Right</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Forward</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2094
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Undoes</action> a <quote>Go Back</quote> action."
msgstr "<action>Razveljavi</action> dejanje <quote>Nazaj</quote>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2098
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>Home</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Home</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>Home</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Home</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:2105
#, no-c-format
msgid "Changes to the users home folder, &eg; /home/Peter/."
msgstr "Spremembe uporabnikove domače mape, &eg; /home/Peter/."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2110
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Recently Closed Tabs</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Nedavno zaprti zavihki</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:2114
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shows a list of recently closed tabs which can be reopened."
msgstr "Prikaže seznam nedavno zaprtih zavihkov, ki jih lahko ponovno odprete."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2122
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Tools Menu"
msgstr "Meni Orodja"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F4</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Open Terminal</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F4</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Odpri terminal</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:2134
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens &konsole; within the current folder."
msgstr "Odpre &konsole; v trenutni mapi."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Open Preferred "
"Search Tool</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Odpri "
"prednostno orodje za iskanje</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:2145
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens preferred search tool in the current folder."
msgstr "Odpre prednostno orodje za iskanje v trenutni mapi."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2149
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Compare Files</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Primerjaj datoteki</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:2153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Compare the currently selected files or folders with &kompare;. This action "
"is only enabled if two files or folders are selected."
msgstr ""
"Primerja trenutno izbrane datoteke ali mape s funkcijo &kompare;. To dejanje "
"je omogočeno le, če sta izbrani dve datoteki ali mapi."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2158
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Select Remote Charset</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Izberi oddaljeni nabor znakov</"
"guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:2162
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allows you to choose the charset used by a remote connection manually."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča ročno izbiro znakovne lestvice, ki se uporablja v oddaljeni povezavi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2170
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings and Help Menu"
msgstr "Meni Nastavitve in pomoč"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2171
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&dolphin; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> and "
"<guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the sections "
"about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"&dolphin; ima skupna elementa menija &kde; <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> in "
"<guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu>, za več informacij preberite poglavja o <ulink url="
"\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">Meni Nastavitve</ulink> in "
"<ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help\">Meni Pomoč</ulink> "
"iz &kde; Osnove."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2182
#, no-c-format
msgid "Miscellaneous Questions"
msgstr "Različna vprašanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2187
#, no-c-format
msgid "Has &dolphin; replaced &konqueror;?"
msgstr "Je &dolphin; nadomestil &konqueror;?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2190
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&dolphin; is not intended to be a competitor to &konqueror;: &konqueror; "
"acts as a universal viewer being able to show &HTML; pages, text documents, "
"folders and a lot more, whereas &dolphin; focuses on being only a file "
"manager. This approach allows the optimization of the user interface for the "
"task of file management."
msgstr ""
"&dolphin; ni mišljen kot konkurent &konqueror;ja: &konqueror; deluje kot "
"univerzalni pregledovalnik, ki lahko prikazuje strani &HTML;, besedilne "
"dokumente, mape in še veliko več, medtem ko se &dolphin; osredotoča le na "
"upravitelja datotek. Ta pristop omogoča optimizacijo uporabniškega vmesnika "
"za nalogo upravljanja datotek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2201
#, no-c-format
msgid "How can I get involved with the development of &dolphin;?"
msgstr "Kako se lahko vključim v razvoj projekta &dolphin;?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The easiest way to get involved with &dolphin; is to subscribe to the "
"developer mailing list <ulink url=\"https://mail.kde.org/mailman/listinfo/"
"kfm-devel\">kfm-devel</ulink> and drop an email to the developer mailing "
"list. Email what you can do, how much time you can devote &etc;, the "
"developers will let you know what you can do in the project. If you wish to "
"contribute to the documentation please email the <ulink url=\"mailto:kde-doc-"
"english@kde.org\">&kde; Documentation Team</ulink> list."
msgstr ""
"Najlažji način sodelovanja z &dolphin; je, da se naročite na poštni seznam "
"razvijalcev <ulink url=\"https://mail.kde.org/mailman/listinfo/kfm-devel"
"\">kfm-devel</ulink> in pošljete e-poštno sporočilo na poštni seznam "
"razvijalcev. Pošljite e-pošto, kaj lahko storite, koliko časa lahko namenite "
"in podobno; razvijalci vam bodo sporočili, kaj lahko storite v projektu. Če "
"želite prispevati k dokumentaciji, pišite na seznam <ulink url=\"mailto:kde-"
"doc-english@kde.org\">&kde; ekipa za dokumentacijo</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2217
#, no-c-format
msgid "How can I submit bug reports?"
msgstr "Kako lahko oddam poročila o napakah?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The official channel for submitting bug reports is via the &kde; bug "
"tracking system. The &kde; bug tracker can be found at <ulink url=\"https://"
"bugs.kde.org\">https://bugs.kde.org</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Uradni kanal za pošiljanje poročil o napakah je sistem za sledenje napakam "
"&kde;. Sledilnik napak &kde; najdete na <ulink url=\"https://bugs.kde.org"
"\">https://bugs.kde.org</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2230
#, no-c-format
msgid "How can I submit feature requests?"
msgstr "Kako lahko oddam zahteve za funkcije?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The official channel for submitting feature requests is via the &kde; bug "
"tracking system. The &kde; bug tracker can be found at <ulink url=\"https://"
"bugs.kde.org\">https://bugs.kde.org</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Uradni kanal za oddajo zahtevkov za funkcije je sistem za sledenje napakam "
"&kde;. Sledilnik napak &kde; najdete na <ulink url=\"https://bugs.kde.org"
"\">https://bugs.kde.org</ulink>."

